F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fjeremy-siegel-inflation-high-falling-prices-fed-rate-hike-prediction-2022-9%5C%22%3Epush%20the%20economy%20into%20a%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEl-Erian%2C%20for%20his%20part%2C%20has%20been%20a%20loud%20critic%20of%20the%20Fed's%20monetary%20tightening%20over%20the%20past%20year.%20Previously%2C%20he%20said%20the%20US%20faced%20an%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0IjML8hrBN0%5C%22%3Euncomfortably%20high%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20probability%20of%20a%20downturn%2C%20though%20the%20central%20bank%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates%20prematurely.%20That%20could%20risk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Frecession-warning-stagflation-economist-mohamed-el-erian-bank-crisis-inflation-2023-4%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMohamed%2520El%252DErian%2520said%2520the%2Cnot%2520easily%2520countered%2520by%2520policies.%2522%5C%22%3Einflation%20expectations%20spiraling%20out%20of%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20slamming%20the%20economy%20with%20a%20far%20more%20serious%20stagflation%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-inflation-economy-cpi-july-data-2023-8%5C%22%3EPrices%20accelerated%203.2%25%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20down%20significantly%20from%20the%20peak%20of%209.1%25%20hit%20last%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20El-Erian%20warned%20that%20inflation%20could%20rebound%20over%20the%20short-term%2C%20thanks%20to%20persistent%20services%20inflation%20and%20wage%20inflation.%20That%20could%20result%20in%20the%20Fed's%20inflation%20target%20quietly%20drifting%20to%203%25%20as%20central%20banks%20are%20forced%20to%20tolerate%20higher-than-ideal%20prices%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-broken-mortgage-rates-supply-demand-mohamed-el-erian-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693249412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63593decdf449200194517dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-broken-mortgage-rates-supply-demand-mohamed-el-erian-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20from%20record-low%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20levels%20that%20we%20haven't%20seen%20for%20almost%2020%20years%2C%20you've%20destroyed%20both%20demand%20and%20supply%2C%26quot%3B%20El-Erian%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40insider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Fhousing-market-broken-mortgage-rates-supply-demand-mohamed-el-erian-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20Centre%20Can%20Conduct%20Caste%20Census%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Told%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20a%20section%20of%20its%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20other%20body%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20Census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20now%20dropped%20the%20said%20paragraph.%20The%20development%20came%20after%20the%20controversial%20paragraph%20drew%20sharp%20reactions%20from%20some%20Bihar%20leaders%20as%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20caste%20survey%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20mentions%20that%20under%20the%20Census%20Act%2C%20only%20the%20Government%20is%20empowered%20to%20conduct%20a%20census.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20government%2C%20in%20an%20earlier%20hearing%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20an%20exercise%20of%20conducting%20surveys%20of%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20the%20state%20was%20conducted%20by%20August%206%20and%20the%20data%20gathered%20uploaded%20by%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20came%20a%20week%20after%20the%20top%20court%20allowed%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20representing%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20file%20its%20response%20on%20the%20issue%20within%20seven%20days%20after%20he%20said%20the%20survey%20could%20have%20some%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBihar%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20has%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20filing%20the%20affidavit.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20no%20knowledge.%20They%20only%20know%20how%20to%20lie%20and%20suppress%20the%20truth.%20They%20have%20opposed%20it%20even%20in%20the%20affidavit.%20It%20has%20been%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20it%20(caste%20census)%20and%20is%20opposing%20it.%20If%20they%20support%20it%2C%20then%20they%20should%20conduct%20it%20(caste%20census)%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20Sushil%20Modi%2C%20however%2C%20said%20that%20his%20party%20supports%20caste%20census%20but%20%26quot%3Baccording%20to%20the%20Census%20Act%2C%20only%20the%20Centre%20can%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20said%20that%20it%20is%20committed%20to%20taking%20all%20affirmative%20actions%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bupliftment%20of%20SCS%2FSTS%2FSEBCs%20and%20OBCs%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20and%20the%20applicable%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarious%20petitions%20have%20been%20moved%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court%20judgment%20upholding%20the%20caste%20survey%20ordered%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20August%2021%20hearing%2C%20the%20top%20court%20told%20the%20petitioners%20that%20it%20would%20not%20stay%20the%20exercise%20unless%20they%20made%20out%20a%20prima%20facie%20case%20again