since%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Fannie%20Mae%2C%20the%20other%20government-backed%20mortgage%20finance%20giant%2C%20serious%20delinquencies%20fell%20to%200.54%25%20in%20July%20from%200.55%25%20in%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20edition%20of%20his%20newsletter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcalculatedrisk.substack.com%2Fp%2Ffannie-mae-single-family-mortgage%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalculated%20Risk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20veteran%20real%20estate%20expert%20Bill%20McBride%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20is%20the%20lowest%20rate%20since%20before%20the%20housing%20bust%20of%202008%2C%20as%20well%20as%20below%20the%20pre-pandemic%20low%20of%200.60%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFreddie's%20serious%20delinquency%20rate%20peaked%20in%20February%202010%20at%204.20%25%20following%20the%20housing%20bubble%20and%20peaked%20at%203.17%25%20in%20August%202020%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20McBride%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22949%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Single%20Family%20Serious%20Delinquency%20Rates%2C%20Calculated%20Risk%20Blog%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecd12710a2ec00199f54ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22717%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESingle%20Family%20Serious%20Delinquency%20Rates%3Cp%3ECalculated%20Risk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decline%20in%20serious%20delinquencies%20point%20to%20low%20rates%20of%20foreclosures%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20suggest%20stable%20prices.%20Homes%20that%20are%20sold%20in%20foreclosure%20are%20often%20priced%20lower%2C%20as%20lenders%20are%20aiming%20to%20make%20their%20money%20back.%20The%20dynamic%20was%20on%20display%20in%202008%2C%20when%20a%20wave%20of%20bank%20foreclosures%20dragged%20the%20US%20housing%20market%20down%2C%20with%20prices%20plummeting%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%2C%20too%2C%20that%20the%20numbers%20from%20Fannie%20Mae%20and%20Freddie%20Mac%20are%20highly%20representative%20of%20the%20US%20mortgage%20market%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20as%20a%20majority%20of%20mortgages%E2%80%9465%25%2C%20by%20the%20Fed's%20calculations%E2%80%94are%20packaged%20into%20mortgage-backed%20securities%20issued%20by%20the%20two%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20the%20delinquency%20numbers%20say%2C%20in%20McBride's%20words%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20lending%20standards%20have%20been%20solid%20and%20most%20homeowners%20have%20substantial%20equity%20there%20will%20not%20be%20a%20huge%20wave%20of%20single-family%20foreclosures%20this%20cycle.%20This%20means%20that%20we%20will%20not%20see%20cascading%20price%20declines%20like%20following%20the%20housing%20bubble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcBride%2C%20who%20Business%20Insider%20has%20profiled%20in%20the%20past%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-mcbride-of-calculated-risk-2012-11%5C%22%3Ethe%20inventor%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20economics%20blogosphere%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20publishes%20regular%20housing%20market%20updates%20ranging%20from%20trend%20pieces%20to%20more%20granular%20data%2C%20such%20as%20delinquency%20rates%20or%20multifamily%20starts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-home-price-affordable-real-estate-property-finance-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693248070000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecce4710a2ec00199f51d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fhousing-market-outlook-home-price-affordable-real-estate-property-finance-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rate%20of%20mortgage%20payments%20more%20than%2090%20days%20late%20dipped%20below%20levels%20seen%20before%20the%202008%20housing%20crash.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22prosen%40insider.com%20(Phil%20Rosen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fhousing-market-outlook-home-price-affordable-real-estate-property-finance-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Govt%20Defensive%20Over%20Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%2C%20Changes%20Affidavit%20in%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-2022-02-07-at-8.25.47-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20filed%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20late%20on%20Monday%20evening%20noting%20that%20a%20certain%20paragraph%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98previous%E2%80%99%20affidavit%20had%20%E2%80%9Cinadvertently%20crept%20in%E2%80%9D.%20The%20paragraph%20in%20question%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20other%20body%20under%20the%20Constitution%20or%20otherwise%20is%20entitled%20to%20conduct%20the%20exercise%20of%20either%20census%20or%20any%20action%20akin%20to%20census.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20affidavit%20comes%20following%20criticism%20from%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%20They%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20neither%20wants%20to%20conduct%20a%20census%20nationally%20nor%20does%20it%20want%20Bihar%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Union%20government%20dropping%20para%205%20from%20the%20previous%20affidavit%20and%20filing%20a%20fresh%20affidavit%2C%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20view%20on%20the%20matter%20remains%20the%20same.%20The%20new%20affidavit%20says%20that%20a%20census%20is%20a%20statutory%20process%20governed%20by%20the%20Census%20Act%20of%201948%2C%20which%20was%20enacted%20in%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20under%20Entry%2069%20of%20List%20I%20of%20the%20Constitution%E2%80%99s%20Seventh%20Schedule%20and%20that%20the%20said%20Act%20empowers%20only%20the%20Central%20Government%20to%20conduct%20the%20Census%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbihar-caste-survey-case-state-govt-census-centre-tells-supreme-court-236420%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20was%20eager%20to%20convey%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20in%20any%20way%20obstructing%20the%20Bihar%20census%2C%20when%20he%20told%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20was%20neither%20opposing%20nor%20supporting%20the%20litigation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20move%20came%20shortly%20after%20Bihar%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20had%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20no%20knowledge.%20They%20only%20know%20how%20to%20lie%20and%20suppress%20the%20truth.%20They%20have%20opposed%20it%20even%20in%20the%20affidavit%E2%80%A6%20It%20has%20been%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20it%20and%20is%20opposing%20it.%20If%20they%20support%20it%2C%20then%20they%20should%20conduct%20it%20(caste%20census)%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fani%2Fstatus%2F1696182944719925418%3Fs%3D46%26t%3D1vwSP919utJCl83SiqVxmg%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20RJD%20patriarch%20and%20former%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20had%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%20on%20the%20issue.%20He%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20a%20hostile%20attitude%20towards%20the%20caste%20survey%20conducted%20in%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%20of%20this%20country%20seems%20distressed%20with%20castes.%20He%20keeps%20mentioning%20%E2%80%98Jati%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20speeches%2C%20perhaps%20he%20thinks%20this%20social%20reality%20will%20not%20let%20him%20enjoy%20peace.%20He%20is%20right%20if%20he%20thinks%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F26%2Fmodi-govt-hostile-towards-caste-survey-in-bihar-lalu-prasad-2608977.html%5C%22%3Ehe%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20say%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20followed%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20said%20they%20are%20for%20the%20caste%20census%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20on%20the%20backfoot%20and%20anxious%20to%20evade%20the%20subject.%20It%20has%20problems%20with%20agreeing%20to%20do%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20as%20it%20is%20fundamentally%20at%20odds%20with%20its%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20seeking%20%E2%80%98vertical%20integration%E2%80%99%20of%20all%20castes%20under%20a%20Hindutva%20umbrella%20and%20also%20not%20suitable%20for%20it%20politically.%20It%20feels%20such%20a%20survey%20will%20only%20benefit%20the%20Opposition%20speaking%20of%20empowerment%20and%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%20is%20complete%2C%20similar%20surveys%20are%20being%20conducted%20in%20Odisha%20and%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20launched%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20stating%20that%20detailed%20information%20on%20the%20socio-economic%20conditions%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20state%20would%20help%20create%20better%20government%20policy%20to%20aid%20disadvantaged%20groups.%20The%20entire%20exercise%20was%20supposed%20to%20have%20been%20completed%20by%20May.%20However%2C%20the%20legal%20challenges%20meant%20the%20government%20was%20unable%20to%20complete%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693247806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F07202552%2FScreenshot-202