-plus-series-fear-walking-dead-1235706198%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Fdigital%2Fnews%2Fmax-amc-plus-series-fear-walking-dead-1235706198%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Article%2035A%20Robbed%20J%26amp%3BK%20Non-Residents%20Of%20Fundamental%20Rights%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArticle%2035A%20of%20the%20Constitution%20has%20deprived%20people%20not%20residing%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20of%20some%20key%20constitutional%20rights%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20said%20today.%20Equality%20of%20opportunity%2C%20employment%20in%20the%20state%20government%20and%20right%20to%20buy%20land%20--%20%26quot%3Ball%20this%20this%20article%20snatches%20away%20from%20citizens...%20Because%20the%20residents%20(of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20had%20special%20rights%2C%20the%20non-residents%20were%20excluded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20also%20agreed%20with%20the%20Centre%20that%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20is%20a%20document%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20higher%20platform%20than%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20observations%20came%20during%20the%2011th%20day%20of%20hearing%20of%20the%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20granted%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20its%20special%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2035A%2C%20which%20was%20also%20scrapped%20in%20August%202019%20along%20with%20Article%20370%2C%20allowed%20the%20legislature%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20to%20define%20%26quot%3Bpermanent%20residents%26quot%3B%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20special%20rights%20and%20privileges%20in%20terms%20of%20public%20employment%2C%20immovable%20property%20and%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20direct%20right%20under%20Article%2016(1)%20which%20was%20taken%20away%20was%20employment%20under%20the%20state%20government.%20Employment%20under%20the%20State%20Government%20is%20specifically%20provided%20under%20Article%2016(1).%20So%20while%20on%20the%20one%20hand%20Article%2016(1)%20was%20preserved%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Article%2035A%20directly%20took%20away%20that%20fundamental%20right%20and%20was%20protected%20from%20any%20challenge%20on%20this%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Article%2019%20recognizes%20the%20right%20to%20live%20and%20settle%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BHence%20all%20the%20three%20fundamental%20rights%20were%20essentially%20taken%20away%20by%2035A...%20Power%20of%20judicial%20review%20was%20taken%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20has%20been%20one%20of%20Centre's%20key%20arguments%20in%20scrapping%20the%20special%20status%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnArguing%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Centre%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20said%20the%20move%20has%20put%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20on%20par%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20It%20implements%20all%20those%20welfare%20laws%20which%20were%20not%20implemented%20earlier%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20example%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20constitutional%20amendment%20that%20added%20Right%20to%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20amendment%20made%20to%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20would%20not%20apply%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20until%20it%20was%20invoked%20through%20Article%20370%E2%80%A6%20So%20Right%20to%20Education%20was%20never%20implemented%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20till%202019%2C%20because%20this%20route%20was%20not%20followed%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chadrachud%20cited%20Mr%20Mehta's%20earlier%20example%20of%20the%20amendment%20of%20the%20Preamble.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20secularism%20and%20socialism%20amendment%20was%20never%20adopted%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3