der%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20department%20is%20in%20frequent%20communication%20with%20servicers%20to%20ensure%20it%20is%20delivering%20timely%20information%20to%20borrowers%20about%20the%20payment%20resumption.%20The%20department%20has%20also%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-forgiveness-cheaper-payments-more-fsa-funding-congress-2023-5%5C%22%3Eacknowledged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20funding%20from%20Congress%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20limits%20the%20resources%20it%20can%20allocate%20to%20implement%20new%20programs%20quickly%20and%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it's%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20to%20ensure%20they%20can%20financially%20plan%20for%20the%20payment%20resumption%2C%20and%20these%20technical%20issues%20are%20not%20making%20matters%20easier.%20One%20borrower%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnewjerseyavenue%2Fstatus%2F1696192232376644085%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20that%20%26quot%3BI've%20finally%20gathered%20the%20courage%20to%20look%20at%20my%20student%20loans%20and%20figure%20out%20a%20game%20plan%20(very%20triggering)%20and%20yet%20the%20website%20is%20completely%20not%20working%E2%80%A6how%20is%20this%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20another%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOrienteMadison%2Fstatus%2F1696209029154918622%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Byour%20systems%20are%20down%20days%20before%20student%20loan%20interest%20restarts.%20Trying%20to%20login%20to%20my%20account%20to%20start%20repayment%20planning.%20Houston%2C%20we%20have%20a%20serious%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20experiencing%20challenges%20with%20the%20student-loan%20payment%20resumption%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20student%20debt%3F%20Reach%20