s%20first%20pertinent%20to%20understand%20whether%20the%20problem%20is%20cyclical%20or%20structural%20in%20nature.%20That%20clarity%20can%20help%20avoid%20the%20fallout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20China%20has%20emerged%20relatively%20unscathed%20from%20the%20Asian%20financial%20crisis%20and%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20even%20managed%20to%20somehow%20stay%20afloat%20until%202023%2C%20despite%20the%20US-China%20trade%20war%20since%202017.%20This%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20such%20crises%20are%20cyclical%20in%20nature%20and%20are%20inherently%20in%20the%20DNA%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy.%20Yet%20a%20closer%20examination%20would%20reveal%20that%20the%20crisis%20in%202023%20is%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ones%20that%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20has%20tackled%20in%20the%20past%20and%20is%20actually%20structural%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Politburo%20meeting%20in%20July%2C%20China's%20leaders%20referred%20to%20the%20economic%20recovery%20this%20year%20as%20%26quot%3Btorturous%26quot%3B.%20What%20they%20were%20referring%20to%20was%20China's%20current%20economic%20problems%2C%20which%20range%20from%20slowing%20GDP%20growth%20rates%20to%20massive%20unemployment%2C%20to%20deeply%20entrenched%20inequality%2C%20to%20dangerously%20low%20levels%20of%20consumption%20among%20others.%20The%20interesting%20point%20to%20note%20is%20that%20such%20candour%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20from%20a%20communist%20party%20institution%2C%20let%20alone%20from%20such%20an%20elevated%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumer%20prices%20in%20July%20were%20lower%20than%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20suggesting%20that%20it%20might%20be%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20deflation%2C%20which%20reflects%20a%20chronic%20shortage%20of%20demand%20in%20the%20economy.%20Foreign%20trade%20in%20the%20same%20month%20showed%20a%20sharp%20fall%20in%20exports%2C%20owing%20to%20weak%20global%20demand%2C%20with%20a%20sharper%20decline%20in%20imports%20signifying%20weaknesses%20in%20demand%20at%20home.%20Private%20firms%20and%20entrepreneurs%20are%20also%20not%20spending%20much%20on%20investment%20or%20on%20hiring%20people.%20Youth%20unemployment%20has%20topped%2021%25%20or%20thrice%20the%20rate%20in%20the%20US.%20Clearly%2C%20most%20things%20currently%20weighing%20on%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20have%20been%20building%20up%20for%20years%2C%20even%20while%20China%20was%20wowing%20the%20world%20with%20its%20magical%20double-digit%20growth%20rates%20and%20claiming%20to%20be%20making%20strides%20in%20lifting%20millions%20out%20of%20poverty%20while%20simultaneously%20moving%20up%20the%20technology%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20prongs%20of%20Chinese%20economic%20development%20since%20Deng%20Xiaoping's%20reforms%20and%20opening%20up%20since%201978%20have%20been%20an%20export-led%20growth%20strategy%20along%20with%20investment.%20The%20reforms%20led%20to%20an%20improvement%20in%20the%20living%20standards%20of%20consumers%20in%20China%2C%20with%20greater%20buying%20capacity%20and%20greater%20demand%20for%20goods%20and%20services%3B%20investment%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20particularly%20in%20export-driven%20enterprises%20in%20the%20coastal%20belts%20of%20China%20also%20brought%20in%20revenues%20driving%20Chinese%20growth.%20Nevertheless%2C%20as%20compared%20to%20consumption%20levels%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20China's%20consumption%20rates%20have%20been%20generally%20low.%20Currently%2C%20consumption%20-%20a%20big%20driver%20of%20growth%20indices%20-%20is%20even%20further%20subdued%20in%20China%2C%20especially%20in%20big-ticket%20items%20such%20as%20cars%2C%20houses%2C%20and%20private%20investment.%20In%20fact%2C%20all%20three%20segments%2C%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%2C%20fell%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20drive%20consumption%2C%20the%20National%20Development%20and%20Reform%20Commission%20(NDRC)%20even%20came%20out%20with%2012%20wide-ranging%20measures%20to%20boost%20domestic%20consumption%2C%20which%20include%20encouraging%20market%20entities%20to%20apply%20domestic%20AI%20technologies%20to%20enhance%20the%20levels%20of%20electronic%20products%2C%20improving%20the%20innovation%20capability%20of%20electronic%20products%2C%20cultivating%20new%20growth%20points%20for%20consumption%20and%20so%20on.%20Clearly%2C%20something%20is%20amiss%2C%20otherwise%20a%20wide-ranging%20agenda%20for%20driving%20consumption%20from%20the%20NDRC%20would%20not%20have%20come%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsumption%20is%20tied%20to%20income.%20As%20stated%20previously%2C%20youth%20unemployment%20alone%20has%20topped%2021%25%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20now%20stated%20it%20will%20stop%20publishing%20data%20on%20youth%20unemployment.%20Without%20employment%2C%20there%20is%20no%20income.%20Without%20income%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20consume.%20But%20beyond%20consumption's%20ties%20to%20income%2C%20there%20also%20are%20other%20structural%20reasons%20why%20consumption%20has%20been%20generally%20low%20while%20savings%20rates%20have%20always%20been%20extraordinarily%20high%20in%20China.%20In%20fact%2C%20China%20has%20an%20extraordinarily%20high%20savings%20rate%20at%20about%2050%25%20of%20its%20GDP.%20The%20reason%20is%20its%20desire%20to%20save%20for%20a%20rainy%20day%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20is%20driven%20by%20bad%20policies%20historically.%20The%20disastrous%20Great%20Leap%20Forward%20and%20Cultural%20Revolution%20driving%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20to%20the%20pits%20under%20Mao%20Zedong%20taught%20Chinese%20consumers%20to%20save%20and%20invest%20in%20land%2C%20which%20they%20can%20liquidate%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disasters%20like%20the%20ones%20Mao%20made%20the%20Chinese%20people%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20under%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20the%20arduous%20three-year%20lockdown%2C%20during%20which%20the%20Chinese%20consumer%20went%20through%20drastic%20lows%20including%20lack%20of%20adequate%20food%20and%20medical%20care%2C%20yet%20again%20spelled%20out%20the%20lesson%20that%20it%20is%20better%20to%20save%20for%20a%20rainy%20day%20rather%20than%20to%20consume.%20Because%20of%20the%20hedonistic%20policies%20carried%20out%20under%20repressive%20regimes%2C%20China%20now%20has%20a%20huge%20local%20government%20debt%20problem%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20bubble%2C%20and%20huge%20creation%20of%20urban%20infrastructures%20accompanied%20by%20under-urbanisation%20-%20all%20of%20which%20indicate%20the%20desire%20to%20save%20rather%20than%20to%20spend%20and%20consume.%20Increasing%20authoritarianism%20under%20Xi%20has%20only%20led%20to%20a%20further%20failure%20of%20the%20development%20model%20which%20once%20shined%20bright%2C%20blinding%20the%20audience%20to%20its%20underlying%2C%20structural%20flaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20this%20mean%20for%20neighbour%20India%3F%20India%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20global%20economy%20and%20reduced%20trade%20with%20China%20will%20lead%20to%20India%20needing%20a%20rethink%20of%20its%20strategies.%20But%2C%20beyond%20the%20fears%2C%20reduced%20imports%20into%20China%20could%20also%20be%20a%20push%20to%20actively%20build%20alternative%20supply%20chains.%20The%20top%20three%20items%20of%20import%20from%20China%20are%20broadcasting%20equipment%2C%20integrated%20circuits%2C%20and%20office%20machine%20parts.%20Collaboration%20between%20India%20and%20Taiwan%20has%20begun%20in%20related%20arenas%20and%20this%20could%20be%20a%20push%20for%20expanding%20greater%20economic%20cooperation.%20The%20top%20three%20exports%20from%20India%20to%20China%20are%20refined%20copper%2C%20cotton%20yarn%2C%20and%20petroleum%20oils.%20Reduced%20demand%20from%20China%20does%20not%20mean%20absolute%20doom%20for%20India%2C%20as%20alternate%20markets%20for%20these%20products%20exist%2C%20and%20India%20only%20needs%20to%20strengthen%20its%20strategies%20to%20develop%20these%20markets%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20Indian%20products%20that%20have%20comparative%20advantages%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20like%20generic%20drugs%20or%20IT%20or%20even%20basmati%20rice%2C%20face%20non-tariff%20barriers%20in%20China.%20Further%20reduced%20demand%20from%20China%20for%20these%20segments%20will%20only%20spur%20India%20to%20explore%20other%20markets.%20There%20are%20also%20fears%20that%20falling%20prices%20of%20Chinese%20goods%20will%20increase%20competition%20and%20hurt%20foreign%20companies.%20Indian%20companies%20in%20China%20in%20any%20case%20are%20a%20handful%2C%20so%20this%20fear%20can%20also%20be%20ruled%20out.%20Slower%20economic%20growth%20in%20China%20could%20also%20benefit%20India%2C%20as%20it%20will%20reduce%20competition%20in%20the%20global%20energy%20and%20especially%2C%20natural%20gas%20markets.%20Lower%20prices%20can%20help%20to%20ease%20energy%20price%20pressures%2C%20which%20will%20be%20to%20India's%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693246320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F78bgh10o_china-flag_625x300_12_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-chinas-economic-crises-cyclical-or-structural-4337755%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20China%20is%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20manufacturing%20platform%20of%20the%20world%2C%20concerns%20around%20its%20decelerating%20growth%20in%202023%20have%20triggered%20panic%20waves%20across%20the%20globe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-chinas-economic-crises-cyclical-or-structural-4337755%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-chinas-economic-crises-cyclical-or-structural-4337755%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fare-chinas-economic-crises-cyclical-or-structural-4337755%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Key%20BRICS%20member%20admits%20the%20dollar%20will%20remain%20dominant%20despite%20oil