20operations%20in%20the%20south%2C%20its%20front-line%20soldiers%20continue%20to%20face%20dangers%20from%20the%20air%2C%20with%20guided%20bombs%20being%20among%20their%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20fears.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20communications%20specialist%20in%20Kyiv's%20military%20named%20Oleksandr%20Solonko%20detailed%20the%20ongoing%20fight%20in%20the%20occupied%20Zaporizhzhia%20region%20in%20a%20recent%20X%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolonko1648%2Fstatus%2F1695525388670095804%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethread%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20threat%20posed%20by%20Moscow's%20powerful%20guided%20bombs%2C%20the%20challenges%20of%20battling%20through%20Russia's%20layered%20defenses%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-mining-everywhere-ukraine-explosives-fridges-toys-books-military-engineers-2023-8%5C%22%3Efortifications%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20including%20minefields%2C%20trenches%2C%20tunnels%2C%20and%20anti-tank%20obstacles%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20role%20that%20aerial%20reconnaissance%2C%20coupled%20with%20ranged%20fires%2C%20plays%20in%20hindering%20movement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20soldier%20can%20be%20spotted%20by%20the%20enemy%20from%20far%20away%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20unit%20they%20serve%20in%20or%20the%20topographical%20features%20of%20the%20battlefield%2C%20Solonko%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20personnel%20and%20equipment%20can%20be%20targeted%20and%20fired%20upon%20from%20a%20distance.%20Attempting%20to%20execute%20a%20mission%20under%20complete%20concealment%C2%A0is%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20impossible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTatarigami_UA%2Fstatus%2F1695563964158025974%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etranslation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20remarks%20by%20another%20service%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolonko%20also%20noted%20%26quot%3Bthe%20enemy's%20advantage%20in%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20said%20has%20been%20a%20critical%20factor%20in%20Ukraine's%20armored%20vehicle%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20airspace%20above%20the%20battlefield%20remains%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-air-force-largely-intact-has-operational-problems-in-ukraine-2023-7%5C%22%3Econtested%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%2018%20months%20of%20full-scale%20war%2C%C2%A0but%20early%20in%20the%20counteroffensive%2C%20Russian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussian-aviation-helicopters-cause-headaches-for-ukraine-armored-assaults-counteroffensive-2023-6%5C%22%3Eattack%20helicopter%3C%2Fa%3E%20crews%20found%20they%20could%20strike%20from%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20Ukraine's%20short-range%20air%20defenses.%20Ukrainian%20forces%20have%20since%20gotten%20better%20about%20eliminating%20these%20threats%2C%20but%20others%20remain%2C%20such%20as%20Russian%20aircraft%20that%20can%20release%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shoot-down-russian-planes-f16-glide-bombs-military-2023-5%5C%22%3Eguided%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKAB's%20are%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20fears%2C%26quot%3B%20Solonko%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Russia's%20arsenal%20of%20guided%20bombs.%20%26quot%3BThe%20russians%20use%20them%20extensively.%20I%20can't%20speak%20to%20their%20accuracy%2C%20but%20the%20weaponry%20is%20powerful.%26quot%3B%20The%20Ukrainian%20military%20has%20been%20raising%20concerns%20about%20these%20kinds%20of%20weapons%20for%20months%2C%20identifying%20them%20as%20serious%20threats%20to%C2%A0%20Ukrainian%20operations.%20Some%20of%20these%20bombs%20can%20be%20over%203%2C000%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20attempt%20to%20target%20logistics%20and%20command%20centers%2C%20just%20as%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20fire%20on%20roads%20and%20forward%20defenses%20in%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20aerial%20reconnaissance%20linked%20system%20Orlan-Zala-Supercam%20is%20effective%20and%20causing%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20Solonko%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20several%20different%20types%20of%20Russian%20drones.%20%26quot%3BThey%20identify%20targets%20and%20launch%20%5BLancets%5D%2C%20releasing%20them%20in%20swarms%20along%20with%20KAB's.%20They%20attempt%20to%20break%20through%20and%20hunt%20down%20vehicles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225535%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Servicemen%20of%20the%20128th%20Separate%20Brigade%20of%20Territorial%20Defence%20Forces%20polish%20first%20aid%20skills%20as%20they%20practise%20storming%20enemy%20positions%20during%20a%20tactical%20drill%20in%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20direction%2C%20southeastern%20Ukraine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecc90910a2ec00199f4d2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EServicemen%20of%20the%20128th%20Separate%20Brigade%20of%20Territorial%20Defence%20Forces%20polish%20first%20aid%20skills%20as%20they%20practise%20storming%20enemy%20positions%20during%20a%20tactical%20drill%20in%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20direction%2C%20southeastern%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Ukrinform%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recaptured%20positions%20are%20even%20more%20calibrated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20before%20highlighting%20the%20destruction%20on%20the%20front%20lines.%20%26quot%3BBombs%20are%20not%20spared.%20No%20lack%20of%20mines%20either.%20The%20tree%20line%20where%20one%20of%20the%20crews%20was%20operating%20was%20simply%20leveled.%20Only%20a%20palisade%20remained%2C%20and%20a%20well-made%20trench%20ceased%20to%20be%20usable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESolonko's%20commentary%20came%20just%20after%20Ukrainian%20forces%20raised%20the%20country's%20flag%20in%20Robotyne%2C%20a%20small%20village%20in%20the%20Zaporizhzhia%20region.%20Kyiv's%20defense%20ministry%20officially%20confirmed%20Robotyne's%20liberation%20on%20Monday%20and%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDefenceU%2Fstatus%2F1696153018960433558%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20soldiers%20from%20the%2047th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20detailing%20the%20operation%20to%20capture%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20a%20soldier%20described%20the%20covert%20nighttime%20mission%20to%20raise%20the%20Ukrainian%20flag%20in%20Robotyne.%20He%20said%20Kyiv's%20troops%20approached%20and%20cleared%20a%20building.%20They%20had%20limited%20visibility%2C%20though%2C%20and%20weren't%20sure%20if%20they%20would%20encounter%20any%20traps%2C%20so%20they%20placed%20the%20flag%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%20When%20the%20sun%20came%20up%2C%20they%20realized%20they%20could%20reach%20the%20roof%20so%20they%20changed%20plans%20and%20placed%20the%20flag%20up%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20to%20all%20your%20brothers-in-arms%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20in%20a%20Sunday%20address%20to%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20all%20our%20other%20warriors%20of%20different%20ranks%2C%20from%20different%20units%2C%20who%20are%20doing%20everything%20possible%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20flag%20is%20in%20all%20its%20rightful%20places%2C%20throughout%20the%20territory%20of%20our%20state!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Robotyne%20is%20quite%20small%2C%20its%20capture%20marks%20a%20bright%20moment%20for%20Ukraine%20as%20it%20continues%20to%20make%20slow%20and%20steady%20progress%20amid%20what%20has%20been%20a%20grueling%20and%20bloody%20counteroffensive.%20Clearing%20Russia's%20complex%20and%20well-established%20defensive%20lines%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20painstaking%20task%20for%20Kyiv's%20troops%2C%20preventing%20them%20from%20recapturing%20territory%20at%20a%20quicker%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20those%20who%20are%20'overly%20smart'%20and%20believe%20that%20the%20Ukrainian%20Armed%20Forces%20took%20an%20incredibly%20long%20time%20to%20drive%20the%20Russians%20out%20of%20the%20village%20of%20Robotyne%2C%20they%20must%20have%20missed%20the%20defense%20system%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20overcome%20in%20order%20to%20push%20the%20russians%20away%20from%20the%20Mariupol%20highway%20and%20gradually%20approach%20the%20village%2C%20encircle%20it%2C%20and%20finally%20seize%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20Solonko%20said.%20%26quot%3BTruly%2C%20a%20monumental%20task%20has%20been%20accomplished.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-powerful-bombs-among-biggest-fears-front-line-ukrainian-soldier-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693244830000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ecb929ecb92e001925398e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-powerful-bombs-among-biggest-fears-front-line-ukrainian-soldier-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20counteroffensive%20challenge%20is%20trying%20to%20execute%20a%20mission%20completely%20concealed%2C%20which%20a%20communications%20specialist%20said%20is%20%26quot%3Bmostly%20impossible.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40insider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-powerful-bombs-among-biggest-fears-front-line-ukrainian-soldier-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Racist%20housing%20practices%20left%20Minneapolis%20with%20an%20extreme%20heat%20problem.%20Now%2C%20the%20city%20is%20rushing%20to%20reverse%20the%20lasting%20effects%20of%20environmental%20racism.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-planet%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Ca%20hr