0Shah%20said%20at%20the%20meet%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Goa%20and%20the%20Administrators%20of%20Dadra%20%26amp%3B%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20Daman%20%26amp%3B%20Diu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20states%20should%20work%20towards%20creating%20the%20necessary%20basic%20infrastructure%20and%20capacity%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20other%20ministers%20and%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20new%20laws%20are%20implemented%2C%20not%20only%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20disown%20colonial%20legacies%20but%20also%20ensure%20that%20a%20uniform%20system%20of%20law%20and%20order%20management%20is%20implemented%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrawing%20comparison%20between%20the%20functioning%20of%20NDA%20and%20UPA%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%20between%202014%20and%202023%2C%20a%20total%20of%2023%20meetings%20of%20the%20Zonal%20Councils%20and%2029%20meetings%20of%20its%20Standing%20Committees%20were%20held.%20From%202004%20to%202014%2C%20there%20were%2011%20meetings%20of%20the%20Zonal%20Council%20and%2014%20meetings%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%2C%20he%20said%2C%20gives%20lot%20of%20importance%20to%20working%20of%20Zonal%20Councils.%20%26quot%3BThe%20role%20of%20Zonal%20Council%20may%20have%20been%20of%20giving%20advice%20earlier.%20But%20over%20the%20years%2C%20they%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20significant%20factor%20in%20promoting%20healthy%20bond%20of%20mutual%20understanding%20and%20cooperation%20in%20various%20spheres%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20added%20that%20the%20Zonal%20Council%20is%20an%20important%20platform%20f