%20lead%20intact%20till%20the%20very%20end%20to%20clinch%20the%20gold%2C%20Neeraj%20remains%20unsatisfied%20with%20the%20throw%2C%20although%20elated%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20was%20able%20to%20add%20another%20medal%20to%20his%20trophy%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshad%20Nadeem%2C%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20champion%20with%2087.82%20m%20bagged%20a%20silver%20medal%20while%20Czech%20Republic's%20Jakub%20Vadlejch%20secured%20the%20bronze%20with%20a%20best%20throw%20of%2086.67%20m.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20who%20looked%20a%20bit%20disappointed%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20post-match%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20throw%20more%20than%2090m%20tonight.%20But%20it%20needs%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20puzzle%20to%20be%20there.%20I%20couldn't%20put%20it%20all%20together%20this%20evening.%20Maybe%20next%20time.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%2025-year-old%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20second%20round%20which%20remained%20untouched%20throughout%20the%20final%2C%20he%20still%20yearned%20to%20break%20his%20own%20mark%20and%20take%20it%20further%20in%20his%20final%20throw.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20second%20round%2C%20I%20was%20thinking%20of%20pushing%20myself%20because%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20could%20get%20a%20better%20throw.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20technique%20and%20speed.%20We%20have%20to%20push%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20qualifying%20round.%20There%20was%20only%20a%20single%20day%20for%20recovery%20so%20it%20was%20also%20a%20big%20factor.%20I%20go%20forward%20with%20the%20motivation%20of%20pushing%20myself%20till%20the%20last%20throw%2C%26quot%3B%20Neeraj%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tokyo%20Olympic%20gold%20medallist%20wasn't%20the%20only%20Indian%20competing%20in%20the%20final%2C%20Kishore%20Jena%20(best%20of%2084.77%20m)%20and%20DP%20Manu%20(best%20of%2084.14%20m)%20were%20also%20in%20the%20mix%20and%20finished%20fifth%20and%20sixth%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Neeraj's%20second%20medal%20at%20the%20World%20Championships%20after%20he%20secured%20a%20silver%20in%202022.%20Previously%2C%20Anju%20Bobby%20George%20had%20bagged%20the%20bronze%20for%20the%20country%20in%20the%202003%20World%20Championships%20for%20the%20women's%20long%20jump.%20He%20has%20also%20bagged%20gold%20at%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%202018%20and%20the%20Asian%20Games%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20will%20be%20back%20on%20the%20field%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games%2C%20Hangzhou%20which%20is%20scheduled%20from%20September%2023%20to%20October%208.%20This%20competition%20will%20mark%20the%20final%20major%20competition%20of%20this%20year%20for%20the%2025-year-old%20javelin%20thrower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693240920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fisenqqeo_neeraj-chopra-afp_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fworld-athletics-championships-gold-done-but-90m-mark-eludes-neeraj-chopra-star-opens-up-on-hallowed-target-4334970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neeraj%20Chopra%2C%20who%20looked%20a%20bit%20disappointed%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20the%20post-match%20conference%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20throw%20more%20than%2090m%20tonight.%20But%20it%20needs%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20puzzle%20to%20be%20there.%20I%20couldn't%20put%20it%20all%20together%20this%20evening.%20Maybe%20next%20time.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fworld-athletics-championships-gold-done-but-90m-mark-eludes-neeraj-chopra-star-opens-up-on-hallowed-target-4334970%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fworld-athletics-championships-gold-done-but-90m-mark-eludes-neeraj-chopra-star-opens-up-on-hallowed-targ