lier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20claimed%20Pawan%20Khatri%2C%20and%20Nitesh%20Kohar%2C%20a%20clerk%20in%20the%20ED%2C%20had%20allegedly%20received%20Rs%205%20crore%20as%20bribe%20through%20conduits%20to%20help%20Amandeep%20Singh%20Dhall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20Dhall%20and%20his%20father%20Birender%20Pal%20Singh%20informed%20ED%20officials%20that%20they%20have%20given%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20Praveen%20Vats%2C%20a%20Chartered%20Accountant%2C%20between%20December%202022%20and%20January%202023%20to%20%26quot%3Barrange%20help%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20ED%20investigation%20in%20the%20case%20against%20Dhall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20complaint%20to%20the%20CBI%20dated%20August%207%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20Praveen%20Vats%20and%20Deepak%20Sangwan%2C%20the%20Air%20India%20employee%2C%20had%20taken%20Rs%205%20crore%20from%20Dhall%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20helping%20him%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20money%20laundering%20case%20through%20Pawan%20Khatri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVats%20stated%20that%20of%20the%20amount%20received%20from%20Dhall%2C%2050%20lakhs%20was%20given%20to%20Sangwan%20and%20Khatri%20as%20advance%20as%20demanded%20by%20them%20in%20mid-December%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20alleged%20in%20its%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dhall%20was%20arrested%20in%20March%20this%20year%2C%20his%20father%20demanded%20a%20refund.%20On%20June%2029%2C%20Rs%201%20crore%20was%20returned%20to%20him%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Khatri%2C%20as%20stated%20by%20Vats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%2C%20Vikramaditya%20Singh%20has%20said%20that%20Aman%20Dhall%20had%20approached%20him%20for%20help%20and%20he%20had%20asked%20Vats%20to%20help%20him.%20Vats%20had%20told%20him%20that%20%26quot%3Bafter%20deducting%20expenses%20with%20ED%20officials%20and%20other%20expenses%2C%20remaining%20amount%20will%20be%20divided%20between%20them%20equally%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ED's%20complaint%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3