Fworld%2Fvladimir-putin-will-not-attend-g20-summit-india%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20Friday%20that%20Putin%20would%20not%20be%20travelling%20to%20India%20as%20he%20was%20concentrating%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cspecial%20military%20operation%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20is%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37056%2FPrime%2BMinister%2Bspeaks%2Bwith%2BPresident%2Bof%2Bthe%2BRussian%2BFederation%5C%22%3Ereadout%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20on%20Monday%2C%20August%2028%2C%20announced%20that%20President%20Putin%20%E2%80%9Cconveyed%20his%20inability%E2%80%9D%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%20slated%20to%20be%20held%20on%20September%209-10.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20Russia%20would%20be%20represented%20by%20its%20foreign%20minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20expressing%20an%20understanding%20for%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20decision%2C%20PM%20thanked%20President%20Putin%20for%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20support%20to%20all%20initiatives%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20Presidency%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Indian%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fkremlin.ru%2Fevents%2Fpresident%2Fnews%2F72135%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20conversation%20was%20silent%20on%20the%20absence%20of%20Putin%20from%20the%20G-20%20summit.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20exchange%20of%20views%20was%20also%20held%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20President%20has%20not%20travelled%20outside%20Central%20Asia%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20in%20February%202022.%20The%20only%20exception%20was%20a%20visit%20to%20Tehran%20in%20July%202022%2C%20where%20he%20also%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20Turkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan.%20He%20also%20didn%E2%80%99t%20attend%20the%20last%20G