the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20only%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20conduct%20a%20census%2C%20and%20no%20other%20body%20is%20entitled%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20similar%20exercise.%20This%20comes%20in%20response%20to%20petitions%20challenging%20a%20caste-based%20survey%20conducted%20in%20Bihar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcensus-act-empowers-only-central-government-to-conduct-census-centre-informs-sc%2Farticleshow%2F103145298.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Law%20Gives%20Right%20To%20Husband%20To%20Beat%2C%20Torture%20Wife%3A%20Delhi%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENo%20law%20gives%20the%20right%20to%20a%20husband%20to%20beat%20and%20torture%20his%20wife%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20held%20while%20granting%20divorce%20to%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20cruelty%20and%20desertion%20by%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20said%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20it%20has%20been%20proved%20that%20the%20man%20failed%20to%20resume%20companionship%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20not%20only%20did%20there%20exist%20physical%20separation%20but%20it%20was%20also%20coupled%20with%20%26quot%3Banimus%26quot%3B%20of%20not%20bringing%20her%20back%20to%20the%20matrimonial%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20into%20account%20the%20medical%20documents%20of%20the%20woman%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20rebuttal%20by%20the%20man%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20held%20that%20the%20woman's%20testimony%20of%20being%20subjected%20to%20physical%20assault%20stands%20corroborated%20by%20the%20medical%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMerely%20because%20the%20parties%20got%20married%20and%20the%20respondent%20(man)%20was%20her%20husband%2C%20no%20law%20gave%20him%20the%20right%20to%20subject%20his%20wife%20to%20beatings%20and%20torture.%20Such%20conduct%20of%20the%20respondent%20necessarily%20qualifies%20as%20physical%20cruelty%20entitling%20the%20appellant%20(woman)%20to%20divorce%20under%20Section%2013(1)%20(ia)%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%20(HMA)%2C%201955%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20man%2C%20who%20was%20present%20before%20it%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20verdict%2C%20had%20no%20objection%20to%20the%20grant%20of%20divorce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20accordingly%20find%20merit%20in%20the%20appeal%20and%20the%20marriage%20between%20the%20appellant%20and%20the%20respondent%20is%20hereby%20dissolved%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20was%20hearing%20an%20appeal%20filed%20by%20the%20woman%20challenging%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20family%20court%20which%20had%20dismissed%20her%20petition%20seeking%20divorce%20from%20the%20man%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20cruelty%20and%20desertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20woman%20had%20deposed%20that%20she%20was%20left%20at%20her%20parental%20home%20on%20May%2011%2C%202013%2C%20in%20an%20injured%20condition%20and%20thereafter%20despite%20her%20efforts%2C%20the%20man%20refused%20to%20take%20her%20back%20to%20the%20matrimonial%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20man%20has%20also%20not%20countered%20the%20woman's%20argument%20that%20she%20was%20not%20brought%20back%20to%20the%20matrimonial%20home%2C%20for%20which%20there%20existed%20no%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20proved%20that%20the%20respondent%20had%20failed%20to%20resume%20the%20companionship%20with%20the%20appellant%20and%20thus%20not%20only%20there%20exist%20physical%20separation%20but%20it%20was%20also%20coupled%20with%20'animus'%20of%20not%20bringing%20back%20the%20appellant%20to%20the%20matrimonial%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20respondent%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20resuming%20the%20matrimonial%20relationship%20which%20also%20got%20reflected%20when%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20petition.%20The%20petition%20for%20divorce%20has%20been%20filed%20after%20more%20than%20two%20years%20of%20separation%20and%20therefore%20the%20appellant%20is%20also%20entitled%20to%20divorce%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20desertion%20under%20Section%2013%201%20(ib)%20of%20the%20HMA%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20woman's%20plea%2C%20she%20and%20the%20man%20got%20married%20in%20February%202013%20and%20they%20have%20been%20living%20with%20the%20family%20of%20the%20man's%20maternal%20aunt%20since%20his%20parents%20died%20a%20long%20time%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20that%20soon%20after%20the%20marriage%2C%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20physical%20and%20mental%20torture%20and%20various%20atrocities%20were%20meted%20out%20to%20her%20which%20she%20continued%20to%20tolerate%20in%20the%20fond%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20passage%20of%20time%2C%20things%20would%20get%20settled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20atrocities%20of%20the%20man%20and%20his%20family%20members%20kept%20increasing%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20her%20so%20that%20the%20man%20could%20re-marry%20into%20an%20affluent%20family%2C%20the%20plea%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20repeated%20demand%20for%20dowry%20and%20she%20was%20deserted%20by%20the%20man%20who%20refused%20to%20take%20her%20back%20to%20the%20matrimonial%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693236300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2Ft72t3c1g_delhi-high-court-650_625x300_11_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2