0look%20forward%20to%20it.%20When%20difficulty%20comes%20in%20front%20of%20you%20get%20excited.%20You%20don't%20shy%20away%20from%20it.%20After%2015%20years%20I%20still%20like%20encounters%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Cup%202023%20is%20one%20(challenge).%20It%20excites%20me%2C%20I%20need%20something%20new%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20propel%20me%20to%20another%20level%2C%26quot%3Bsaid%20Kohli%20during%20a%20promotional%20event%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20did%20not%20deny%20that%20there%20is%20pressure%20of%20expectations%20on%20him%20and%20the%20team.%20But%20Kohli%20reminded%20everyone%20that%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup%20more%20than%20the%20players%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pressure%20is%20always%20there.%20The%20fans%20always%20say%20we%20want%20(the%20team)%20to%20win%20a%20cup%20very%20badly.%20I'd%20like%20to%20say%20not%20more%20than%20me.%20So%2C%20I'm%20in%20the%20right%20place.%20Honestly%2C%20I%20know%20the%20expectations%20are%20there%20and%20the%20emotions%20of%20the%20people%20are%20there.%20But%20please%20know%20that%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20win%20more%20than%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%2C%20though%2C%20is%20no%20stranger%20to%20winning%20a%20World%20Cup.%20He%20had%20led%20India%20to%20the%20ICC%20U-19%20World%20Cup%20victory%20back%20in%202008%20and%20he%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20MS%20Dhoni-led%20India%20side%20that%20triumphed%20in%20the%202011%2050-over%20World%20Cup%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20career%20highlight%20%C3%AFs%20obviously%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%20I%20was%2023%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20I%20probably%20didn't%20understand%20the%20magnitude%20of%20it.%20But%20now%20at%2034%2C%20and%20has%20played%20many%20World%20Cups%2C%20which%20we%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20win%2C%20So%2CI%20understand%20the%20emotions%20of%20all%20the%20senior%20players%20(in%202011).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20more%20for%20Sachi