urbs%20on%20All%20Varieties%20of%20Rice%20India%20Ships%20Overseas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20latest%20curbs%20on%20the%20export%20of%20basmati%20rice%2C%20a%20day%20after%20a%2020%25%20duty%20was%20levied%20on%20parboiled%20rice%2C%20India%20has%20now%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20every%20variety%20of%20the%20grain%20that%20it%20ships%20overseas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20introduced%20a%20%241200%20price%20floor%20on%20the%20export%20of%20Basmati%20rice%20to%20keep%20a%20check%20on%20non-basmati%20exports%20which%20are%20prohibited%20but%20were%20being%20exported%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20Basmati%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20said%20in%20a%20notification%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CContracts%20of%20Basmati%20rice%20below%20%241200%20a%20tonne%20may%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance%20and%20may%20be%20evaluated%20by%20a%20committee%20to%20be%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Chairman%20of%20APEDA%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20government%20notification.%20The%20Agricultural%20and%20Processed%20Food%20Products%20Export%20Development%20Authority%20(APEDA)%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20regulation%20of%20Basmati%20rice%20exports%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fforeign-trade%2Fbasmati-rice-exports-contracted-at-a-price-lower-than-1200-a-ton-temporarily-halted-govt%2Farticleshow%2F103102267.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minimum%20export%20rice%20would%20help%20authorities%20ensure%20that%20non-basmati%20rice%20is%20not%20exported%20as%20basmati%20rice%2C%20said%20the%20notification.%20The%20latest%20restrictions%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20an%20impact%20across%20the%20global%20market%2C%20with%20benchmark%20rice%20prices%20in%20Asia%20near%20the%20highest%20level%20in%20almost%2015%20years%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2025%2C%20the%20government%20had%20levied%20a%2020%25%20duty%20on%20the%20export%20of%20non-Basmati%20parboiled%20rice%20which%20accounted%20for%2030%25%20of%20rice%20shipments%20in%202021-2022%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverseas%20sales%20of%20non-Basmati%20white%20grain%20were%20halted%20last%20month%2C%20with%20the%20caveat%20that%20some%20shipments%20would%20be%20allowed%20if%20requested%20to%20meet%20the%20food%20security%20needs%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20India%20banned%20overseas%20sales%20of%20the%20broken%20variety%20which%20also%20accounted%20for%20about%2020%25%20of%20shipments%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20ships%20out%20around%204%20million%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20basmati%20rice%20to%20countries%20such%20as%20Iran%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Yemen%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Economic%20Times%20reported.%20It%20saw%20record%20exports%20in%20FY22%20and%20FY23%20because%20of%20Indian%20rice%20still%20being%20cheaper%20than%20other%20varieties%2C%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcentre-imposes-conditional-curbs-on-basmati-rice-export-11693116550422.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693233895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F03164309%2FDSC2224-1024x684-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fafter-basmati-exports-centre-places-curbs-on-all-varieties-of-rice-india-ships-overseas%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20introduced%20a%20%241200%20price%20floor%20on%20the%20export%20of%20Basmati%20rice%2C%20a%20day%20after%20a%2020%25%20duty%20was%20levied%20on%20parboiled%20rice.%2