%20of%20the%20centenary%20of%20Nandamuri%20Taraka%20Rama%20Rao%20or%20NTR%2C%20cinestar%2C%20ex-chief%20minister%2C%20a%20powerful%20political%20force%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20function%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20shows%20the%20attention%20the%20Union%20government%20would%20like%20to%20draw%20to%20his%20legacy%20and%20its%20desire%20to%20get%20associated%20with%20it%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20one%20family%20member%20who%20was%20kept%20out%20%E2%80%93%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20office%20did%20not%20send%20an%20invite%20to%20his%20wife%2C%20Nandamuri%20Laksmi%20Parvathi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2025%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Fandhrapradesh%2Fcentre-to-release-special-coin-in-honour-of-ntr%2F%5C%22%3ELakshmi%20Parvathi%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Murmu%20and%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cseeking%20their%20intervention%20to%20instruct%20the%20concerned%20officials%20to%20include%20her%20name%20in%20the%20guest%20list%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%2C%20Lakshmi%20Parvathi%20mentioned%20that%20she%20was%20married%20to%20the%20late%20NTR%20on%20September%2011%2C%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20we%20led%20a%20peaceful%20family%20life%20and%20actively%20participated%20in%20the%20%5BAndhra%20Pradesh%5D%20state%20legislature%20election%20in%201994.%20Under%20our%20leadership%2C%20the%20TDP%20secured%20226%20assembly%20seats%20out%20of%20294.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20a%20conspiracy%20orchestrated%20by%20his%20elder%20son-in-law%20Nara%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20in%20collusion%20with%20other%20family%20members%2C%20power%20was%20acquired%20through%20backdoor%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20further%20quoted%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20unfortunate%20turn%20of%20events%20led%20to%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20deep%20depression%2C%20as%20he%20expressed%20his%20dissatisfaction%20with%20his%20children%E2%80%99s%20families.%20Tragically%2C%20he%20passed%20away%20on%20January%2018%2C%201996.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20very%20same%20family%20members%20who%20were%20responsible%20for%20his%20demise%20are%20now%20invited%20to%20the%20prestigious%20function%20of%20releasing%20the%20%E2%82%B9100%20coin%20in%20his%20memory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvathi%20further%20stated%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20First%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20single%20woman%2C%20I%20wish%20to%20express%20my%20profound%20dissatisfaction%20with%20the%20authorities%20responsible%20for%20this%20oversight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaJONyQaW48Y%26ab_channel%3DNTVLive%5C%22%3Esharply%20criticised%20the%20political%20morality%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20state%20BJP%20president%20D.%20Purandeswari%20in%20a%20video%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fmovies%2Fntr-rs-100-coin-released-by-president-of-india-droupadi-murmu-video-goes-viral-8553943.html%5C%22%3Esons%2C%20daughters%20and%20other%20extended%20relatives%20of%20NTR%20were%20invited%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20function%20and%20the%20Rs%20100%20coin%20has%20the%20inscription%20%E2%80%981923-2023%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FNandamuriTarakaRamarao%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23NandamuriTarakaRamarao%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gari%20%E2%82%B9100%20Coin%20officially%20launched%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%20at%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20Delhi%20TODAY.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FJoharNTR%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23JoharNTR%3C%2Fa%3E%20%F0%9F%99%8F%F0%9F%99%8F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2