.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENTR%E2%80%99s%20first%20wife%20Basavatarakam%20died%20in%201985.%20His%20second%20wife%2C%20a%20writer%20whom%20he%20married%20in%201993%2C%20is%20said%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20politics%20and%20public%20life%2C%20and%20also%20resented%20by%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20likely%20that%20her%20being%20in%20the%20picture%20now%20could%20complicate%20any%20political%20project%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20claim%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20political%20inheritance.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20others%20in%20the%20family%20are%20also%20unlikely%20to%20be%20easy%20if%20she%20were%20to%20be%20acknowledged.%20Sources%20say%20this%20may%20be%20the%20reason%20she%20was%20simply%20left%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1952850%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20speaking%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20commemorative%20coin%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20president%20said%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20late%20Shri%20N.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20has%20enriched%20Indian%20cinema%20and%20culture%20through%20Telugu%20films.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%C2%A0breathed%20life%20into%C2%A0the%C2%A0prominent%C2%A0characters%20of%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20through%20his%20acting.%20The%20characters%20of%20Lord%20Rama%20and%20Lord%20Krishna%20played%20by%20him%20became%20so%20alive%20that%20people%20started%20worshiping%20NTR.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurmu%20is%20also%20said%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Cnoted%20that%20NTR%20also%20expressed%20the%20pain%20of%20the%20common%20people%20through%20his%20acting.%20He%20spread%20the%20message%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20equality%20through%20one%20of%20his%20films%20titled%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EManushulanta%20Okkate%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20i.e.%20All%20human%20beings%20are%20equal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20also%20spoke%20flatteringly%20about%20NTR%E2%80%99s%20film%20and%20political%20legacy%20and%20remarked%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cinitiated%20many%20public%20welfare%20programmes%2C%20which%20are%20remembered%20till%20today%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693233059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28182941%2FNTR-coin.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-release-of-ntr-coin-wife-not-present%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attention%20showered%20on%20NTR%20on%20his%20birth%20centenary%20is%20indicative%20of%20the%20BJP's%20desire%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20his%20political%20legacy.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20hailed%20the%20late%20actor%20for%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20prominent%20characters%20of%20the%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20through%20his%20acting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fat-release-of-ntr-coin-wife-not-present%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20INDIA%20Set%20For%20Next%20Round%20Of%20Meet%2C%20Due%20In%20Mumbai%20By%20Month-End%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20Bloc%20INDIA%20will%20have%20its%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031%20and%20September%201%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20announced.%20The%20party%20will%20host%20the%20meet%2C%20where%20the%20united%20Opposition%20is%20expected%20to%20draft%20its%20Common%20Minimum%20Programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20expectation%20that%20an%2011-member%20coordination%20committee%20will%20also%20be%20named%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20we%20will%20decide%20on%20who%20the%2011%20will%20be%2C%20who%20the%20Convenor%20will%20be%2C%20etc.%20These%20are%20small%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Congress's%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meet%20comes%20days%