he%20young%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20requested%20the%20pilot%20to%20divert%20to%20Nagpur%20(in%20Maharashtra).%20On%20landing%2C%20we%20ensured%20the%20child's%20stables%20were%20vital%20and%20handed%20her%20over%20to%20a%20paediatrician%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20told%20NDTV.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20stressful...%20the%20child%20did%20not%20revive%20at%20first%20and%20we%20had%20to%20work%20for%2045%20minutes%20without%20giving%20up%20hope.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAlways%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Always%3C%2Fa%3E%20available%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FAIIMSParivar%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23AIIMSParivar%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20returning%20from%20ISVIR-%20on%20board%20Bangalore%20to%20Delhi%20flight%20today%20evening%2C%20in%20Vistara%20Airline%20flight%20UK-814-%20A%20distress%20call%20was%20announced%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20a%202%20year%20old%20cyanotic%20female%20child%20who%20was%20operated%20outside%20for%20intracardiac%20repair%20%2C%20was%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FcrDwb1MsFM%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FcrDwb1MsFM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20AIIMS%2C%20New%20Delhi%20(%40aiims_newdelhi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Faiims_newdelhi%2Fstatus%2F1695872850911981988%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EFortunately%20for%20the%20child%2C%20she%20had%20five%20excellent%20doctors%20on%20her%20flight%20and%20also%20an%20AED%2C%20or%20automated%20external%20defibrillator.%20An%20AED%20is%20a%20portable%20electronic%20device%20that%20delivers%20an%20electric%20shock%20through%20the%20chest%20to%20the%20heart%20when%20it%20detects%20an%20abnormal%20rhythm%2C%20and%20restores%20th