23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Putin%20will%20not%20travel%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20broke%20last%20week%20after%20the%20Kremlin's%20statement%20on%20the%20Russian%20leader%2C%20who%20faces%20global%20criticism%20for%20leading%20his%20country%20into%20the%20war%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20(ICC)%20has%20issued%20an%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20Vladimir%20Putin%3B%20it%20accuses%20him%20of%20war%20crimes%20in%20Ukraine%20-%20something%20the%20Kremlin%20has%20strongly%20denied.%20The%20ICC's%20warrant%20means%20Mr%20Putin%20risks%20arrest%20when%20travelling%20abroad%20and%20that%20was%20one%20reason%20why%20he%20did%20not%20travel%20to%20South%20Africa%20(for%20the%20BRICS%20Summit)%20either%2C%20preferring%20instead%20to%20address%20the%20meeting%20via%20a%20video%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-brics-summit-putins-justifies-war-with-ukraine-4322521%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAt%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20Putin's%20Justifies%20War%20With%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20as%20speculation%20mounted%2C%20the%20Russian%20envoy%20to%20India%2C%20Denis%20Alipov%2C%20said%20a%20decision%20on%20who%20would%20represent%20his%20country%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20would%20be%20made%20shortly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20my%20prerogative...%20I%20would%20suggest%20we%20wait%20for%20the%20official%20announcement.%20As%20regards%20his%20(Putin's)%20participation%20in%20the%20G20%20and%20what%20format%20it%20will%20be%20(and)%20who%20is%20going%20to%20represent%20Russia%20at%20the%20summit...%20I%20think%20such%20an%20announcement%20will%20be%20made%20shortly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693232100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvim