0force%20to%20co-found%20Yunikee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Chaithanya%2C%20an%20IT%20professional%2C%20it%20was%20watching%20his%20wife%20Nita%E2%80%99s%20work%20ethic%20while%20she%20taught%20deaf%20kids%2C%20which%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20him.%20So%2C%20after%20a%2025-year-long%20stint%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Chaithanya%20quit%20his%20job%20in%202020%20to%20join%20Nita%20in%20creating%20the%20social%20impact%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20their%20vision%20was%20Rahul%2C%20an%20ISL%20teacher%20who%20had%20been%20working%20with%20Nita%20since%202017%20teaching%20deaf%20kids%20in%20special%20schools.%20Being%20deaf%2C%20Rahul%20brought%20unique%20insights%20to%20the%20table%20on%20how%20they%20could%20formulate%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20cater%20to%20solving%20some%20vital%20problems%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F22762%2Fmy-story-3000-children-born-deaf-now-communicate-with-parents%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20experiencing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201174px)%20100vw%2C%201174px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221174%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Yunikee%20caters%20to%20thousands%20of%20deaf%20young%20adults%20through%20campaigns%2C%20programs%20and%20activities%20that%20teach%20ISL%20(Indian%20Sign%20Language)%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187.jpg%201174w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187-300x178.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187-500x297.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187-768x456.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyunikee-1-1693225187-150x89.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328342%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22697%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EYunikee%20caters%20to%20thousands%20of%20deaf%20young%20adults%20through%20campaigns%2C%20programs%20and%20activities%20that%20teach%20ISL%20(Indian%20Sign%20Language)%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaithanya%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20conversation%20sparks%20an%20idea%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20every%20day%20that%20three%20people%20from%20very%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20bond%20over%20an%20idea.%20As%20Chaithanya%2C%20Nita%20and%20Rahul%20share%20the%20story%20of%20Yunikee%E2%80%99s%20inception%2C%20they%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20incredible%20alignment%20of%20thoughts%2C%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20thanks%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaithanya.%20The%20trio%20was%20discussing%20the%20unfairness%20of%20the%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20how%20abled%20students%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20continuing%20their%20schooling%20online%20while%20students%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145157%2Fahmedabad-ngo-proves-deaf-blindedness-doesnt-hinder-learning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20denied%20this%20basic%20right.%20They%20figured%20that%20this%20discrimination%20extended%20beyond%20the%20classroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20if%20we%20were%20to%20start%20a%20platform%20that%20enabled%20hearing%20disabled%20people%20to%20access%20equal%20opportunities%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs%2C%20skillset%20training%20and%20more%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%