pUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Pakistan-India%20Rivalry...%26quot%3B%3A%20Arshad%20After%20Neeraj%20Pipped%20Him%20For%20Gold%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20Arshad%20Nadeem%2C%20India's%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20will%20have%20tough%20competition%20for%20the%20gold%20medal%20at%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20but%20the%20Pakistani%20ace%20says%20for%20now%20both%20are%20just%20%26quot%3Bvery%20happy%26quot%3B%20to%20call%20the%20shots%20in%20a%20sport%20once%20dominated%20by%20the%20Europeans.%20In%20cricket-crazy%20Pakistan%2C%20Nadeem%20has%20become%20the%20toast%20of%20the%20nation%20after%20becoming%20its%20first%20athlete%20to%20win%20a%20medal%20at%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships.%20Nadeem%20bagged%20silver%20in%20the%20men's%20javelin%20thrown%20final%20in%20Budapest%20on%20Sunday%2C%20as%20Olympic%20champion%20Chopra%20won%20the%20gold%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeeraj%20and%20I%20have%20a%20very%20healthy%20competition%20and%20we%20respect%20each%20other%20a%20lot.%20There%20is%20no%20Pakistan-India%20rivalry%20in%20a%20bad%20way.%20When%20we%20talk%20we%20are%20just%20happy%20that%20both%20of%20us%20have%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20a%20competition%20usually%20dominated%20by%20Europeans%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadeem%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20first%20medal%20that%20Nadeem%20has%20brought%20home%20as%20last%20year%20he%20won%20gold%20in%20the%20Birmingham%20Commonwealth%20Games%20with%20a%20best%20throw%20of%2090.18%20metres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Nadeem%2C%20the%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%20Worlds%20was%20very%20satisfying%20as%20he%20competed%20against%20Chopra%2C%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20couldn't%20compete%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%20because%20of%20a%20groin%20injury%20and%20Arshad%20ran%20away%20with%20the%20gold%20in%20a%20field%20dominated%20by%20European%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20final%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Chopra%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20invite%20his%20Pakistani%20rival%20to%20go%20on%20a%20victory%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20satisfying%20achievement%20for%20me%20to%20get%20a%20distance%20of%2087.82%20metres%20as%20I%20returned%20to%20international%20competition%20after%20nearly%20a%20year%20due%20to%20my%20elbow%20surgery%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rivalry%20between%20Chopra%20and%20Nadeem%20has%20now%20become%20a%20subject%20of%20discussion%20in%20the%20javelin%20fraternity.%20What%20was%20unique%20on%20Sunday%20was%20that%20the%20first%20time%20both%20Pakistani%20and%20Indian%20athletes%20were%20in%20the%20limelight%20at%20the%20same%20time%20in%20the%20World%20Championships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Nadeem%20won%20the%20silver%20medal%2C%20there%20were%20calls%20on%20social%20media%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20ensure%20he%20is%20duly%20rewarded%20for%20his%20achievement%2C%20with%20the%20caretaker%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Anwaar-ul-Haq-Kakar%2C%20being%20the%20first%20to%20congratulate%20him%20on%20his%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Nadeem%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long%20journey%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Mian%20Chunnu%20in%20Pakistan's%20Punjab%20province%20where%20his%20elder%20brothers%20and%20school's%20sports%20master%20forced%20him%20to%20take%20up%20athletics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20cricketer%20but%20my%20brothers%20and%20sports%20master%20told%20me%20I%20had%20the%20physique%20and%20stamina%20to%20be%20a%20top%20athlete%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20early%20days%2C%20he%20would%20sprint%20around%202-3%20kilometres%20everyday%20from%20his%20village%20to%20school%2C%20something%20that%20helped%20him%20strengthened%20his%20body%20alongside%20the%20hard%20work%20he%20put%20in%20the%20fields%20with%20his%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20humble%20background%2C%20the%20sudden%20adulation%20has%20not%20affected%20Nadeem%20as%20he%20remains%20focussed%20on%20his%20goal%20to%20win%20a%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20Paris%20Games%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20gold%20for%20my%20country.%20It%20will%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%2C%20training%20and%20the%20best%20equipment%20but%20now%20I%20know%20I%20am%20capable%20of%20doing%20well%20against%20the%20best.%26quot%3B%20Like%20many%20of%20his%20contemporaries%2C%20Nadeem%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20top%20coaches%2C%20foreign%20training%20and%20the%20best%20equipment%2C%20as%20the%20Pakistan%20Athletics%20Federation%20is%20always%20short%20on%20funds%20and%20the%20country%20does%20not%20have%20top-class%20training%20facilities%20for%20javelin%20throwers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20Nadeem%20is%20grateful%20to%20his%20employee%2C%20Wapda%2C%20which%20have%20provided%20him%20with%20coaches%20and%20facilities%20to%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693228440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Flk6bc17g_neeraj-chopra-arshad-nadeem_650x300_28_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fno-pakistan-india-rivalry-arshad-nadeem-after-neeraj-chopra-pipped-him-at-world-athletics-championships-4336290%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Neeraj%20Chopra%20inched%20Pakistan's%20Arshad%20Nadeem%20in%20the%20javelin%20throw%20final%20to%20bag%20his%20maiden%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20World%20Athletics%20Championships%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Fno-pakistan-india-rivalry-arshad-nadeem-after-neeraj-chopra-pipped-him-at-world-athletics-championships-4336290%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2