e%20away.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20the%20song%20is%20that%20some%20of%20the%20lyrics%20seem%20so%20universal%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20damn%20shame%20what%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20gotten%20to%2C%20for%20people%20like%20me%2C%20for%20people%20like%20you%2C%20wish%20I%20could%20just%20wake%20up%20and%20it%20not%20be%20true.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsqSA-SY5Hro%3Fsi%3DTLS-vV4Ub3_jPWq6%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20or%20not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20US%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20what%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20another%20unsavoury%20long-haul%20of%20political%20manoeuvring%20before%20the%20presidential%20election%20in%20November%202024%2C%20Anthony%20has%20grabbed%20the%20hearts%20of%20millions%20by%20cutting%20to%20the%20chase%20about%20his%20view%20of%20the%20political%20and%20economic%20elite%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20rich%20men%20north%20of%20Richmond%E2%80%A6they%20all%20just%20wanna%20have%20total%20control%2C%20wanna%20know%20what%20you%20think%2C%20wanna%20know%20what%20you%20do%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20Anthony%20takes%20digs%20at%20some%20of%20the%20other%20downtrodden%20in%20the%20US%3A%20%E2%80%9CLord%2C%20we%20got%20folks%20in%20the%20street%2C%20ain%E2%80%99t%20got%20nothing%20to%20eat%2C%20And%20the%20obese%20milkin%E2%80%99%20welfare%E2%80%A6Taxes%20ought%20not%20to%20pay%2C%20for%20your%20bags%20of%20fudge%20rounds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20invokes%20the%20widespread%20notion%20in%20the%20US%20that%20people%20receiving%20state%20financial%20assistance%20are%20merely%20feeding%20off%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20song%E2%80%99s%20title%20and%20lyrics%20also%20give%20voice%20to%20the%20common%20argument%20that%20Americans%20in%20the%20South%2C%20and%20many%20in%20poor%20rural%20areas%2C%20have%20been%20left%20behind%20by%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20a%20guy%20with%20a%20guitar%20and%20his%20dogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Richmond%20in%20%E2%80%98Rich%20Men%20North%20of%20Richmond%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20the%20southeastern%20US%20state%20of%20Virginia%2C%20where%20Anthony%20resides.%20It%20is%20also%20just%20a%20few%20hours%E2%80%99%20drive%20south%20of%20the%20US%20capital%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fus-capitol-riot-committee-subpoenas-secret-service%2Fa-62496900%5C%22%3Epolitical%20hub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20RADIOWV%20YouTube%20channel%20featuring%20Anthony%E2%80%99s%20songs%2C%20he%20lives%20in%20the%20aptly%20named%20small%20town%20of%20Farmville%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20his%203%20dogs%20and%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20he%20plans%20on%20turning%20into%20a%20small%20farm%20to%20raise%20livestock.%E2%80%9D%20Indeed%2C%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98Rich%20Men%20of%20Richmond%E2%80%99%20video%2C%20he%20can%20be%20seen%20singing%20outdoors%20in%20a%20wooded%20area%2C%20with%20a%20hunting%20hut%20up%20in%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20background%20and%20a%20camping%20stool%20to%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20cites%20Hank%20Williams%20Jr.%20as%20his%20biggest%20musical%20influence.%20RADIOWV%20wrote%20on%20YouTube%20that%3A%20%E2%80%9COliver%20wants%20to%20give%20hope%20to%20the%20working%20class%20and%20your%20average%20hard-working%20young%20man%20who%20may%20have%20lost%20hope%20in%20the%20grind%20of%20trying%20to%20get%20by.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoliticians%20seize%20the%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20loaded%20political%20climate%20in%20the%20US%2C%20some%20politicians%20have%20seized%20on%20Anthony%E2%80%99s%20perceived%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepublican%20Congresswoman%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Greene%2C%20from%20the%20southern%20state%20of%20Georgia%20and%20who%20has%20a%20history%20of%20supporting%20far-right%20conspiracy%20theories%2C%20said%20on%20the%20platform%20X%20(formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter)%20that%20Anthony%E2%80%99s%20song%20is%20one%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20Washington%20DC%20needs%20to%20hear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20Democratic%20Senator%20Chris%20Murphy%20of%20the%20northeastern%20state%20of%20Connecticut%20also%20said%20that%20left-leaners%20should%20heed%20Anthony%E2%80%99s%20call%2C%20writing%20on%20the%20same%20social%20media%20platform%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprogressives%20should%20listen%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20adding%20that%20the%20track%20%E2%80%9Cshows%20the%20path%20of%20realignment.%20Anthony%20sings%20about%20the%20soullessness%20of%20work%2C%20shit%20wages%20and%20the%20power%20of%20the%20elites.%20All%20problems%20the%20left%20has%20better%20solutions%20to%20than%20the%20right.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnthony%20himself%20has%20called%20his%20political%20views%20%E2%80%9Cpretty%20dead%20centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20concert%20he%20played%20in%20North%20Carolina%20on%20Saturday%2C%20August%2019%2C%20he%20told%20Fox%20News%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20our%20country%20lasting%20another%20generation%20the%20way%20we%20are%20headed.%20We%20got%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20roots%20of%20what%20made%20this%20country%20great%20in%20the%20first%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnthony%20claims%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20spotlight%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20singer%20and%20former%20factory%20worker%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Christopher%20Anthony%20Lunsford%2C%20adopted%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20name%20%E2%80%9COliver%20Anthony%E2%80%9D%20as%20his%20stage%20name.%20He%20has%20been%20writing%20music%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20despite%20his%20huge%20popularity%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20he%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20in%20no%20hurry%20to%20sign%20a%20record%20deal%3A%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20the%20music%20industry%20give%20me%20blank%20stares%20when%20I%20brush%20off%208%20million%20dollar%20offers%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0he%20wrote%20on%20Facebook%2C%20saying%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20go%20on%20large%20tours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20in%20the%20spotlight.%20I%20wrote%20the%20music%20I%20wrote%20because%20I%20was%20suffering%20with%20mental%20health%20and%20depression.%20These%20songs%20have%20connected%20with%20millions%20of%20people%20on%20such%20a%20deep%20level%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20being%20sung%20by%20someone%20feeling%20the%20words%20in%20the%20very%20moment%20they%20were%20being%20sung.%20No%20editing%2C%20no%20agent%2C%20no%20bullshit.%20Just%20some%20idiot%20and%20his%20guitar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20August%2017%20Facebook%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Anthony%20has%20already%20inspired%20other%20musicians.%20Across%20the%20pond%2C%20British%20punk-turned-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ffrom-bob-dylan-to-bruce-springsteen-why-song-rights-sales-are-booming%2Fa-57435772%5C%22%3Efolk-singer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20labour%20rights%20activist%20Billy%20Bragg%20released%20on%20August%2021%20on%20YouTube%20his%20own%20response%20to%20Anthony%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Rich%20Men%E2%80%99%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0reported%20on%20Bragg%E2%80%99s%20video%20introduction%20to%20his%20%E2%80%9Ccorrective%E2%80%9D%20response%20song%20to%20Anthony%2C%20in%20which%C2%A0he%20says%20that%C2%A0he%20felt%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20ghost%20of%20%5Blate%20US%20folk%20artist%5D%20Woody%20Guthrie%20whispering%20in%20my%20ear.%20%E2%80%98Help%20that%20guy%20out%2C%E2%80%99%C2%A0Woody%20keeps%20telling%20me.%20%E2%80%98Let%20him%20know%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20thos