ilm's%20victory%20a%20%26quot%3Bmockery%20of%20film%20awards%26quot%3B.%20A%20section%20of%20filmmakers%20from%20the%20Southern%20part%20of%20the%20country%20felt%20Dalit-themed%20films%20were%20neglected%20as%20some%20of%20the%20most%20potent%20and%20popular%20films%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3EJai%20Bhim%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESarpatta%20Parambarai%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKarnan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20failed%20to%20make%20the%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202017%20win%20of%20Akshay%20Kumar%20for%20his%20performance%20in%20%3Cem%3ERustom%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20contenders%20included%20Aamir%20Khan%20for%20%3Cem%3EDangal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20jury%20president%2C%20Priyadarshan%2C%20who%20often%20collaborated%20with%20Kumar%2C%20defended%20his%20choice%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20should%20we%20have%20given%20the%20Best%20Actor%20award%20to%20Aamir%20Khan%20when%20he%20has%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20he%20doesn't%20attend%20awards%20functions%3F%20%E2%80%A6%20Nowadays%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20people%20returning%20their%20awards.%20We%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20that%20risk.%26quot%3B%20A%20couple%20of%20years%20later%2C%20Akshay%20Kumar%20hosted%20the%20famous%20interview%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20in%20which%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20the%20national%20fruit%20was%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22t69293ik%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ft69293ik_rustomembed_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EAkshay%20Kumar%20in%20%3Cem%3ERustom%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%20win%20for%20Best%20Actor%20came%20under%20criticism%20as%20his%20mother%2C%20Sharmila%20Tagore%2C%20headed%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Film%20Certification%2C%20which%20works%20under%20the%20same%20ministry%20that%20gives%20away%20the%20awards.%20In%202002%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn's%20award%20for%20Best%20Actor%20created%20a%20controversy%20as%20the%20jury%20was%20headed%20by%20Prakash%20Jha%20who%20was%20directing%20Devgn%20in%20his%20film%20%3Cem%3EGangaajal%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20year%20the%20awards%20were%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20chair%20of%20the%2067th%20National%20Awards%2C%20Vipul%20Amrutlal%20Shah%2C%20went%20on%20to%20produce%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kerala%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%2C%20going%20by%20the%20example%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Files%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20could%20be%20a%20contender%20for%20the%20Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20National%20Integration%20next%20year.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22gmfmrrig%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fgmfmrrig_humtumembed_625x300_28_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%20and%20Rani%20Mukerji%20in%20%3Cem%3EHum%20Tum%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20our%20National%20Awards%20susceptible%20to%20serving%20the%20government's%20ideology%3F%20While%20the%20jury%20selects%20the%20winners%2C%20who%20chooses%20the%20jury%20members%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20the%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Ministry%20through%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Film%20Festivals.%20By%20exercising%20complete%20control%20over%20the%20choice%20of%20jury%20members%2C%20the%20government%20holds%20undue%20and%20unilateral%20power%20over%20the%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20any%20award%20in%20the%20field%20of%20arts%20can't%20claim%20to%20be%20completely%20objective%2C%20a%20certain%20extent%20of%20transparency%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20National%20Awards%2C%20which%20is%20perhaps%20the%20only%20film%20award%20in%20the%20world%20given%20by%20a%20head%20of%20a%20state.%20The%20world%20has%20seen%20the%20recent%20example%20of%20the%20Golden%20Globes%2C%20the%20second-biggest%20film%20award%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20fell%20from%20grace%20because%20it%20failed%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20time%20and%20refused%20to%20be%20inclusive%20and%20representative%20of%20diverse%20voices.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20trajectory%20that%20the%20National%20Film%20Awards%20has%20taken%2C%20one%20might%20ask%2C%20should%20the%20government%20be%20even%20giving%20national%20awards%3F%20Doesn't%20the%20idea%20of%20government-sponsored%20awards%20feel%20like%20an%20instrument%20to%20patronise%20filmmakers%3F%20What%20entitles%20the%20state%20to%20become%20the%20arbitrator%20of%20arts%3F%20And%2C%20if%20the%20state%20is%20to%20decide%20the%20best%20film%20of%20the%20year%2C%20can%20one%20expect%20a%20movie%20to%20win%20the%20honour%20if%20it%20critiques%20the%20state%3F%20Isn't%20art%20supposed%20to%20favour%20truth%20rather%20than%20power%3F%20And%20isn't%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20artists%20a%20prerequisite%20to%20independent%20art%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Film%20Awards%20were%20instituted%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20Film%20Enquiry%20Committee%20constituted%20in%201949.%20It%20was%20headed%20by%20a%20Mumbai%20Congress%20leader%20and%20had%20prominent%20filmmakers%20V%20Shantaram%20and%20B.%20N%20Sircar%20among%20its%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20considered%20various%20questions%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20the%20film%20industry%20should%20be%20nationalised.%20The%20committee%20vehemently%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20nationalisation%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20regimentation%20of%20ideas%20and%20art%20would%20make%20beauty%20subservient%20to%20the%20rule%20of%20thumb%2C%20culture%20submissive%20to%20the%20will%20of%20authority%20and%20entertainment%20subordinate%20to%20the%20philosophy%20of%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20committee%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20nationalisation%20of%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20it%20also%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20giving%20it%20complete%20freedom%20without%20explaining%20any%20reason%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20reject%20this%20method%20of%20approach%20without%20further%20argument%20and%20content%20ourselves%20with%20saying%20that%20virtue%20lies%20in%20owning%20rather%20than%20concealing%20one's%20own%20faults%20and%20shortcomings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20chose%20to%20regulate%20cinema%20with%20a%20stick%20and%20a%20carrot.%20The%20stick%20is%20the%20censor%20board%2C%20which%20can%20deny%20certification%20to%20a%20film%2C%20making%20it%20unfit%20for%20theatrical%20release%20or%20punish%20it%20by%20giving%20an%20%26quot%3BA%26quot%3B%20certificate%2C%20trimming%20its%20business%20potential%20significantly.%20It's%20worth%20a%20note%20that%20a%20filmmaker%20can't%20apply%20for%20the%20national%20awards%20without%20a%20censor%20certificate.%20The%20carrot%20is%20the%20award%20it%20can%20bestow%20upon%20films%20that%20align%20with%20its%20ideology%20by%20fixing%20a%20compliant%20jury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20does%20the%20government%20get%20so%20much%20power%20over%20the%20film%20business%3F%20Why%20doesn't%20the%20industry%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20censors%20or%20awards%3F%20Why%20aren't%20films%20treated%20at%20par%20with%20literature%20or%20fine%20arts%20and%20are%20left%20for%20the%20professionals%20or%20practitioners%20to%20decide%20the%20awards%3F%20Why%20the%20government%20directly%20appoints%20jury%20members%20through%20its%20ministry%20to%20choose%20the%20winners%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20listened%20to%20the%20committee's%20recommendation%20by%20setting%20up%20the%20awards%2C%20it%20ignored%20the%20part%20that%20asked%20for%20a%20representative%20mechanism%20to%20regulate%20the%20film%20industry.%20The%20committee%20gave%20its%20recommendations%20in%201951%2C%20which%20called%20for%20establishing%20a%20Film%20Council%20comprising%20film%20producers%2C%20directors%2C%20artists%2C%20technicians%2C%20distributors%2C%20exhibitors%2C%20educationists%2C%20and%20workers.%20Council%20wasn't%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20bureaucrat%20but%20%26quot%3Ba%20person%20of%20high%20judicial%20status%20and%20commanding%20an%20eminent%20public%20position%20and%20possessing%20a%20depth%20of%20cultural%20background.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20recommended%20council%20to%20oversee%20the%20award%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20the%20government%20set%20up%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Film%20Festivals%20(DFF)%20in%201973%2C%20a%20body%20comprising%20of%20government%20servants%20working%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20government%20directly%20regulating%20the%20industry%20was%20not%20only%20not%20recommended%20by%20the%20committee%2C%20but%20it%20was%20recommended%20against%2C%20%26quot%3B%E2%80%A6we%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20through%20such%20an%20institution%20%5BFilm%20Council%5D%20rather%20than%20through%20its%20own%20agency%20or%20intervention%20that%20the%20Central%20and%20State%20Governments%20can%20succeed%20in%20making%20films%20the%20real%20and%20effective%20instruments%20of%20arts%2C%20culture%20and%20healthy%20entertainment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20government%20listened%20to%20the%20committee's%20many%20suggestions%20and%20set%20up%20film%20schools%2C%20film%20festivals%20and%20national%20awards%2C%20but%20it%20selectively%20ignored%20the%20part%20of%20giving%20a%20fair%20representation%20to%20filmmakers%20in%20the%20process.%20Instead%2C%20the%20government%20chose%20to%20exercise%20uninhibited%20control%20over%20the%20awards.%20The%20system%20worked%20well%20until%20the%20government%20and%20the%20prominent%20filmmakers%20were%20ideologically%20aligned.%20Our%20cinema%20celebrated%20Nehruvian%20socialism%20and%20ideals%20of%20nation-building%2C%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20government%20celebrated%20films%20that%20didn't%20challenge%20its%20ideology.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20government%20always%20had%20the%20upper%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20system%20of%20patronage%20no%20longer%20works%20anymore%20as%20the%20present%20day's%20government%20wants%20to%20propagate%20a%20different%20ideology.%20It%20creates%20an%20avenue%20for%20a%20new%20set%20of%20filmmakers%20ready%20to%20offer%20their%20craft%20for%20the%20cause%20and%20receive%20rewards%20and%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERidiculing%20the%20winners%2C%20calling%20out%20the%20jury's%20incompetence%2C%20or%20even%20terming%20them%20sell-outs%20might%20generate%20noise%20on%20social%20media%2C%20but%20until%20the%20systemic%20flaws%20of%20the%20National%20Film%20Awards%20are%20addressed%2C%20these%20awards%20are%20designed%20to%20reward%20those%20who%20align%20with%20the%20government's%20ideology%2C%20or%20at%20least%2C%20not%20challenge%20it.%20Hence%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20return%20to%20the%20recommendations%20and%20make%20the%20awards%20more%20representative%2C%20transparent%2C%20and%20inclusive.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20function%20of%20any%20award%20is%20to%20accord%20credibility%20to%20the%20work%2C%20the%20National%20Film%20Awards%20are%20bound%20to%20fail%20in%20the%20endeavour%20if%20they%20lack%20credibility%20themselves.%20The%20questionable%20choice%20of%20awards%20calls%20for%20reform%20and%20offers%20an%20opportunity%20to%20start%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20autonomy%20of%20the%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bikas%20Mishra%20is%20an%20award-winning%20writer-director%20based%20in%20Mumbai)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693227000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fi7g413f4_bikas240_120x90_03_July_23.jpg%3Fver-20230818.04%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fopinion-the-national-film-awards-need-reform-4336604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshay%20Kumar's%202017%20win%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan's%202004%20win%20both%20caused%20controversy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%