pulation%2C%20and%2015%20out%20of%2032%20BJP%20MLAs%20%E2%80%93%20including%20eight%20who%20are%20Meitei.%20Pillai%20added%20that%20the%20BJP%20strategy%20means%20that%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20placed%20the%20interests%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20politics%20ahead%20of%20the%20requirements%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20extensive%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Pillai%20said%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20should%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20different%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20crisis%20and%20certainly%20after%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20visit%20in%20late%20May%20had%20failed%20to%20resolve%20the%20crisis.%20Pillai%20said%20Modi%20should%20have%20provided%20a%20healing%20touch%2C%20adding%20this%20is%20what%20the%20%E2%80%9Cemotional%E2%80%9D%20people%20of%20the%20state%20need.%20Pillai%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20could%20have%20done%20this%20by%20visiting%20the%20state%20or%20by%20calling%20key%20people%20to%20Delhi.%20He%20said%20by%20choosing%20not%20to%20do%20this%2C%20Modi%20has%20made%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20wrong%20call%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoiwYwBRakTM%3Fsi%3DCVdrmkJk6vtJo-B8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Pillai%20spoke%20at%20length%20about%20the%20failure%20of%20the%20state%20administration%20to%20restore%20law%20and%20order%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20relief%20and%20rehabilitation.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20points%20he%20made%20is%20the%20state%20administration%20should%20have%20immediately%20acted%20to%20recover%20stolen%20weapons.%20He%20said%20they%20know%20who%E2%80%99s%20got%20them%20and%20they%20should%20have%20%E2%80%9Craided%20houses%E2%80%9D%20to%20get%20them%20back.%20Failure%20to%20do%20so%2C%20he%20added%2C%20suggests%20they%E2%80%99re%20happy%20for%20the%20weapons%20to%20remain%20in%20stolen%20hands.%20Pillai%20also%20said%20all%20the%20officials%20who%20failed%20to%20prevent%20the%20theft%20of%20the%20weapons%20should%20have%20been%20immediately%20punished%20or%20sacked.%20That%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20home%20secretary%20was%20also%20sharply%20critical%20of%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20provide%20rehabilitation%20and%20compensation.%20The%20picture%20he%20paints%20is%20of%20a%20state%20government%20that%20knows%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20but%20is%20failing%20or%20refusing%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPillai%20was%20also%20sharply%20critical%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20response.%20He%20said%20several%20joint%20secretaries%2C%20from%20ministries%20such%20as%20home%2C%20health%20and%20water%20supply%2C%20should%20be%20camping%20in%20Manipur%2C%20to%20ensure%20an%20effective%20response%20but%20have%20not%20been%20sent.%20He%20specifically%20referred%20to%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20promise%2C%20made%20in%20May%2C%20to%20send%20medical%20teams%20which%2C%20three%20months%20later%2C%20remains%20unfulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20has%20not%20seen%20such%20an%20incompetent%20and%20ineffective%20response%20to%20a%20crisis%20in%20his%20entire%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20points%20out%20there%20were%20clear%20warning%20signs%20well%20before%20the%20crisis%20erupted%20on%20May%203%20which%20were%20ignored%20both%20in%20Imphal%20and%20Delhi.%20Again%2C%20this%20points%20to%20the%20incompetence%20of%20the%20people%20in%20charge%20in%20both%20capitals%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20also%20contains%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20of%20what%20Pillai%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cbackground%20issues%E2%80%9D.%20These%20are%20the%20refugees%20seeking%20shelter%20from%20tyranny%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20how%20they%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20factor%20that%20threatens%20demographic%20change%3B%20the%20poppy%20cultivation%20and%20drug%20trade%2C%20in%20which%20he%20says%20both%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20are%20involved%3B%20and%20the%20charge%20of%20forest%20encroachment%2C%20which%20he%20says%20is%20exaggerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPillai%20says%20he%20expects%20relative%20calm%20till%20November-December%20but%20is%20worried%20about%20what%20could%20happen%20thereafter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Pillai%20also%20discusses%20the%20Meitei%20%E2%80%9Cland%20hunger%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20Kuki%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration.%20These%20are%20the%20two%20key%20political%20issues%20that%20are%20most%20difficult%20to%20tackle%20and%20resolve%2C%20he%20said%20and%20gives%20clear%20answers%20to%20how%20they%20should%20be%20handled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20home%20secretary%20also%20puts%20the%20recent%20pro-Kuki%20statements%20by%20the%20United%20Naga%20Council%20in%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693225894000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28175649%2FKT-28-August-2023.01_16_30_20.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-gopal-krishna-pillai-manipur-clashes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20former%20Union%20home%20secretary%20Gopal%20Krishna%20Pillai%20criticised%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20to%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20not%20seen%20such%20an%20incompetent%20and%20ineffective%20response%20to%20a%20crisis%20in%20his%20entire%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-karan-thapar-gopal-krishna-pillai-manipur-clashes%22%2C