.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-lawyers-back-in-dc-court-as-two-sides-differ-over-trial-date-in-election-subversion-case%2Farticleshow%2F103139770.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-lawyers-back-in-dc-court-as-two-sides-differ-over-trial-date-in-election-subversion-case%2Famp_articleshow%2F103139770.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-lawyers-back-in-dc-court-as-two-sides-differ-over-trial-date-in-election-subversion-case%2Famp_articleshow%2F103139770.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Close%20to%2020%25%20of%20Active%20MGNREGS%20Workers%20Ineligible%20For%20Soon-to-be%20Compulsory%20Aadhaar-Based%20Pay%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07101954%2F7655150258_021e6c9ffd_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Close%20to%2020%25%20of%20the%2014%20crore%20active%20workers%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(MGNREGS)%20are%20as%20yet%20ineligible%20to%20be%20paid%20under%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20(ABPS)%2C%20government%20data%20indicates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20accessed%20on%20Monday%20(August%2028)%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnreganarep.nic.in%2Fnetnrega%2F%5C%22%3Escheme%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20that%2011%2C72%2C40%2C317%20(11.7%20crore)%20active%20workers%20are%20currently%20eligible%20to%20be%20paid%20under%20the%20ABPS%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%2014%2C34%2C26%2C231%20(14.3%20crore)%20active%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%202%2C61%2C85%2C914%20(2.6%20crore%20or%20~18%25)%20active%20workers%20who%20are%20ineligible%20to%20be%20paid%20under%20the%20ABPS%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fdeadline-for-mandatory-use-of-aadhaar-based-payment-for-mgnregs-not-to-be-extended-beyond-aug-31%2F1728719%2F%5C%22%3Egovernment%20officials%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20become%20compulsory%20starting%20September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MGNREGS%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20daily%20wage%20employment%20to%20rural%20households%20at%20specially%20notified%20minimum%20wages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20active%20workers%20are%20%E2%80%9Cany%20individuals%20of%20households%20who%20%5Bhave%5D%20worked%20any%20one%20day%20in%20either%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years%20or%20in%20%5Bthe%5D%20current%20financial%20year%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%2C%20workers%20must%20be%20paid%20their%20wages%20for%20any%20given%20day%20of%20work%20within%2015%20days%2C%20failing%20which%20they%20are%20entitled%20to%20additional%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20is%20unclear%20how%20ineligible%20workers%20will%20be%20compensated%20for%20their%20work%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActivists%20say%20it%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20government%20to%20deny%20payment%20to%20ineligible%20workers%20despite%20the%20ABPS%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwenty%20percent%20of%20over%2014%20crore%20workers%20are%20still%20not%20eligible%20for%20payment%20through%20ABPS%3B%20it%20is%20a%20huge%20number.%20Preventing%20payment%20of%20wages%20is%20illegal%20according%20to%20the%20MGNREGA.%20The%202005%20Act%20says%20that%20anyone%20who%20demands%20work%20must%20get%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20activist%20Nikhil%20Dey%20of%20the%20NREGA%20Sangharsh%20Morcha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fgovernance%2Fmodi-govt-makes-aadhaar-based-payments-mandatory-for-nrega-workers-from-1-sept-illegal-say-activists%2F1730060%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThePrint.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20states%20have%20up%20to%20a%20quarter%20of%20their%20active%20MGNREGS%20workers%20still%20ineligible%20to%20receive%20payments%20under%20the%20ABPS.%20