xpress%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cby%20ignoring%20non-active%20workers%2C%20the%20government%20is%20undermining%20their%20constitutional%20right%20to%20work%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F14852243%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F14852243%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F14852243%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20MGNREGS%20worker%20to%20be%20eligible%20under%20the%20ABPS%2C%20their%20job%20card%20and%20bank%20account%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-payments-compulsory-nrega%5C%22%3Emust%20be%20seeded%20with%20their%20Aadhaar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Their%20bank%20account%20must%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(NPCI)%20mapper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20states%20and%20union%20territories%20have%20close%20to%20or%20over%2090%25%20of%20their%20active%20workers%E2%80%99%20Aadhaar%20details%20seeded%20with%20their%20job%20cards%20as%20of%20August%2028%2C%20Assam%2C%20Nagaland%20and%20Meghalaya%20have%20only%2075%25%2C%2045%25%20and%2033%25%20seeding%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20rural%20development%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20dashboard%2C%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20low%20ABPS%20eligibility%20of%203.1%25%20is%20explained%20by%20just%209.5%25%20of%20its%20Aadhaar-verified%20active%20workers%20(who%20number%20about%2031%25%20of%20all%20active%20workers%20in%20the%20state)%20having%20had%20their%20NPCI%20mapping%20process%20completed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20of%20the%20ABPS%20have%20said%20that%20it%20is%20overly%20cumbersome%20and%20may%20deter%20rural%20beneficiaries%20from%20seeking%20work%20under%20the%20MGNREGS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeding%20and%20mapping%20a%20bank%20account%20can%20be%20very%20cumbersome.%20It%20involves%20stringent%20KYC%20requirements%2C%20biometric%20or%20demographic%20authentication%2C%20and%20resolving%20possible%20inconsistencies%20between%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20and%20the%20bank%20account.%20Inconsistencies%20between%20any%20of%20those%20two%20and%20the%20job%20card%20can%20also%20create%20problems%20for%20Aadhaar-based%20payments%20of%20%5BMGNREGS%5D%20wages%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-payments-compulsory-nrega%5C%22%3Eeconomist%20Jean%20Dreze%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20Union%20government%20first%20announced%20the%20ABPS%20would%20become%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FK45FTS6pw8A%3Fsi%3DgWvDjhyYPBrM4gda%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20first%20said%20the%20ABPS%20would%20become%20mandatory%20starting%20February%201%20this%20year%20but%20has%20extended%20the%20deadline%20multiple%20times%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20these%20extensions%20did%20not%20stop%20state%20governments%20%E2%80%9Cracing%20against%20the%20timeline%E2%80%9D%20from%20resorting%20to%20deleting%20the%20job%20cards%20of%20workers%20whose%20card%20and%20Aadhaar%20data%20did%20not%20match%2C%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fthe-use-of-technology-is-nullifying-mgnregas-objective-of-stopping-distress-migration-congress-leader-jairam-ramesh%2Farticle67009149.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChakradhar%20Buddha%2C%20a%20policy%20analyst%20with%20LibTech%20India%2C%20also%20told%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Farticle%2Fwhy-lakhs-nrega-workers-are-still-ineligible-wages-under-aadhaar-based-system-181226%5C%22%3Eworkers%20remain%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20such%20mismatches%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20they%20visit%20a%20job%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COften%2C%20the%20only%20way%20active%20workers%20know%20that%20there%20is%20an%20issue%20with%20their%20job%20card%20is%20when%20they%20turn%20up%20for%20work%20and%20their%20name%20isn%E2%80%99t%20on%20the%20muster%20rolls.%20Until%20then%2C%20they%20are%20unaware%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20simple%20difference%20in%20the%20spelling%20of%20someone%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20or%20the%20incorrect%20gender%2C%20could%20result%20in%20your%20job%20card%20not%20being%20successfully%20authenticated%20with%20your%20Aadhaar%20card.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20multiple%20deadline%20extensions%20since%20February%20this%20year%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported%20government%20sources%20as%20saying%20last%20week%20that%20the%20September%201%20deadline%20will%20not%20be%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Dey%20told%20%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20this%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20only%20result%20in%20deletion%20of%20job%20cards%20and%20people%20being%20denied%20work%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20if%20one%20person%20is%20not%20eligible%20for%20ABPS%20payment%20then%20the%20payment%20of%20the%20entire%20muster%20roll%20%5Bwhich%20has%2010%20people%5D%20will%20get%20affected.%20The%20payment%20is%20released%20for%20all%2010%20in%20one%20transaction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20constituent%20workers%E2%80%99%20unions%20under%20the%20NREGA%20Sangharsh%20Morcha%20will%20send%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20rural%20development%20ministry%20about%20the%20September%201%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693224017000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07101954%2F7655150258_021e6c9ffd_o.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Falmost-twenty-percent-active-nrega-workers-ineligible-abps%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20unclear%20how%20workers%20will%20be%20compensated%20after%20the%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20becomes%20mandatory%20on%20September%201.%20Activists%20say%20it%20would%20be%20illegal%20for%20the%20government%20to%20withhold%20their%20pay.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Falmost-twenty-percent-active-nrega-workers-ineligible-abps%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RIL%20Share%20Price%20Falls%20on%20Lack%20of%20Details%20on%20IPOs%2C%20AGM%20Focussed%20on%20Succession%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F14170421%2Fjio-ambani.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Reliance%20Industries%E2%80%99%20annual%20general%20meeting%20(AGM)%20happened%20on%20August%2028%2C%20Monday%2C%20with%20chairman%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20announcing%20a%20slew%20of%20plans%20for%20the%20conglomerate%20aimed%20at%20strengthening%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20in%20the%20global%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20much-awaited%20event%2C%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Flic-picks-up-6-66-stake-in-jio-financial-services%5C%22%3Etepid%20debut%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Jio%20Financial%20Services%20on%