indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fare-yash-and-prithviraj-sukumaran-lending-their-voices-for-srks-jawan%2Farticleshow%2F103138609.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103138609.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20upcoming%20film%20'Jawan'%2C%20directed%20by%20Atlee%2C%20is%20set%20to%20release%20on%20September%207.%20Reports%20suggest%20that%20actors%20Yash%20and%20Prithviraj%20Sukumaran%20have%20dubbed%20for%20the%20Kannada%20and%20Malayalam%20versions%20of%20the%20film%20respectively.%20The%20trailer%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20released%20today%2C%20and%20fans%20are%20speculating%20about%20who%20will%20be%20dubbing%20in%20Tamil.%20The%20film%20also%20stars%20Nayanthara%2C%20Vijay%20Sethupathi%2C%20and%20Deepika%20Padukone%20in%20special%20roles.%20The%20pre-release%20business%20of%20the%20film%20has%20been%20impressive%2C%20with%20close%20to%20%E2%82%B92%20crore%20earned%20in%20advance%20booking%20in%20the%20USA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fare-yash-and-prithviraj-sukumaran-lending-their-voices-for-srks-jawan%2Farticleshow%2F103138609.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Lies%20Behind%20the%20Rise%20of%20Illegal%20%E2%80%98Firecracker%E2%80%99%20Factories%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28165052%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20locals%20call%20it%20%E2%80%9CBajigram%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20%E2%80%98firecracker%20village%E2%80%99.%20Within%20the%20Nilganj%20village%20of%20Dattapukur%2C%20in%20the%20district%20of%2024%20Parganas%20North%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20illegal%20firecracker%20manufacturing%20has%20evolved%20into%20a%20small-scale%20industry.%20Hundreds%20of%20local%20residents%20and%20individuals%20from%20outside%20the%20area%20work%20as%20daily%20labourers%2C%20engaging%20in%20this%20activity%20without%20any%20safety%20measures%20in%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20around%209%20am%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fwest-bengal-north-24-parganas-firecracker-factory-explosion-deaths-8911630%2F%5C%22%3Epowerful%20explosion%20rocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20activist%20Ajibar%20Rahman%2C%20instantly%20killing%20at%20least%20eight%20people.%20Passersby%20on%20the%20road%20nearby%20were%20also%20knocked%20down.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20adjacent%20houses%20began%20to%20collapse%20one%20after%20the%20other.%20The%20haze%20and%20dust%20generated%20by%20the%20explosion%20took%20nearly%2020%20minutes%20to%20settle.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20the%20concrete%20structure%20of%20the%20house%20had%20transformed%20into%20a%20heap%20of%20rubble.%20The%20force%20of%20the%20blast%20caused%20body%20parts%20of%20the%20factory%20workers%20to%20be%20scattered%20across%20rooftops%20of%20nearby%20houses%2C%20and%20some%20fragments%20even%20landed%20more%20than%20100%20metres%20away.%20The%20explosion%E2%80%99s%20sound%20resonated%20as%20far%20as%20Barasat%20town%2C%20located%20nearly%205%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20site%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20May%2C%20this%20marks%20the%20fifth%20incident%20of%20explosions%20in%20illicit%20firecracker%20facilities%20within%20West%20Bengal%2C%20claiming%20the%20lives%20of%20a%20total%20of%2028%20people.%20On%20May%2016%2C%20another%20explosion%20erupted%20in%20an%20unauthorised%20firecracker%20factory%20situated%20in%20Egra%2C%20Purba%20Medinipur%20district%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20nine%20people.%20Ten%20days%20after%20the%20Egra%20explosion%2C%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20made%20a%20public%20promise%20during%20her%20visit%20to%20the%20site.%20She%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmamata-banerjee-apology-blast-illegal-firecracker-factory%5C%22%3Edeclared%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20government%20would%20take%20stringent%20measures%20against%20illicit%20firecracker%20factories%20and%20introduce%20the%20production%20of%20environmentally%20friendly%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%E2%80%9D%20fireworks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20limited%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20since%20then.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20several%20residents%20in%20Nilganj%20whose%20houses%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20explosion%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20Sunday.%20A%20woman%2C%20who%20preferred%20not%20to%20disclose%20her%20name%20due%20to%20concerns%20about%20repercussions%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20revealed%20that%20previous%20explosions%20had%20occurred%20at%20the%20factory%20as%20well%2C%20but%20they%20went%20unnoticed%20by%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20quite%20a%20few%20instances%20of%20explosions%20in%20that%20factory%20before.%20We%20witnessed%20through%20our%20windows%20the%20sight%20of%20blood-stained%20bodies%20being%20carried%20away.%20Nobody%20knew%20if%20they%20were%20alive%20or%20dead.%20The%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20instructed%20us%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20that%20area.%20The%20police%20stated%20it%20was%20their%20internal%20matter%2C%20and%20outsiders%20should%20not%20interfere.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20all%20neighbouring%20houses%20have%20been%20damaged%20due%20to%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20explosion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20frustration%20among%20the%20local%20residents%20is%20evident%2C%20as%20they%20accuse%20the%20police%20of%20being%20complicit%20in%20shielding%20the%20owners%20of%20illegal%20firecracker%20factories.%20Soon%20after%20the%20explosion%2C%20they%20broke%20into%20a%20chemical%20%E2%80%9Claboratory%E2%80%9D%20within%20a%20nearby%20brick%20kiln%2C%20containing%20substantial%20quantities%20of%20chemicals%2C%20glass%20beakers%2C%20and%20machinery%20that%20they%20allege%20are%20being%20used%20for%20producing%20explosives.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20All%20Bangla%20Fireworks%20Traders%20Association%2C%20Babla%20Roy%2C%20also%20confirmed%20this%20assertion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.anandabazar.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Ffirecracker-or-bomb-experts-initial-probe-on-dattapukur-blast-case-dgtl%2Fcid%2F1455462%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20potassium%20chloride%2C%20a%20significant%20chemical%20in%20creating%20crude%20bombs%20but%20not%20typically%20used%20in%20firecrackers%2C%20was%20indeed%20discovered%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20explosion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20house%20where%20the%20explosion%20occurred%20was%20owned%20by%20Ajibur%20Rahman%2C%20who%2C%20along%20with%20Samsul%20Ali%2C%20operated%20the%20brick%20kiln.%20They%20had%20jointly%20rented%20the%20house%20to%20Keyamat%20Ali%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20blast.%20Both%20Ajibur%20and%20Samsul%20are%20activists%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20purportedly%20the%20reason%20they%20were%20able%20to%20run%20the%20illegal%20work%20even%20though%20the%20police%20were%20aware%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20residents%20with%20whom%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20expressed%20their%20concerns%20about%20such%20factories%20%E2%80%93%20which%20could%20explode%20at%20any%20time%20%E2%80%93%20being%20located%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20densely%20populated%20area.%20They%20claimed%20to%20have%20approached%20the%20police%20multiple%20times%20expressing%20their%20concerns%20and%20seeking%20assistance.%20However%2C%20they%20say%20they%20were%20threatened%20with%20false%20charges.%20As%20per%20the%20locals%2C%20despite%20the%20seizure%20of%20illegal%20firecrackers%20and%20bombs%20worth%20crores%20from%20the%20factory%20owner%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20police%20took%20no%20action.%20Instead%2C%20they%20detained%2018%20villagers%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20the%20factory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20names%20of%20two%20key%20ministers%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20Jyotipriyo%20Mallick%20and%20Rathin%20Ghosh%2C%20have%20emerged%20in%20connection%20with%20these%20allegations%2C%20with%20locals%20asserting%20that%20they%20were%20involved%20in%20supporting%20these%20unlawful%20activities.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20the%20local%20MP%20Kakali%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%2C%20during%20her%20visit%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbangla.hindustantimes.com%2Fbengal%2Fdistricts%2Fnilganj-blast-tmc-kakali-ghosh-dostidar-31693151280658.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereportedly%20warned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20consequences%20for%20individuals%20accusing%20the%20administration%20of%20inaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20there%20for%20campaigning%20during%20the%20panchayat%20election%2C%20but%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20there%20was%20a%20firecracker%20factory%20there.%20I%20know%20of%20one%20in%20Narayanpur.%20This%20was%20an%20ISF%20%5BIndian%20Secular%20Front%2C%20an%20opposition%20party%5D%20conspiracy%20as%20they%20won%20the%20Panchayat%20poll%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rathin%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20food%20and%20supplies%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20locals%20and%20ISF%20leader%20Naushad%20Siddiqui%20denied%20the%20claim.%20Siddiqui%20alleged%2C%20%E2%80%9CBombs%20were%20made%20here%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20betting.%20All%20the%20ministers%20and%20police%20used%20to%20get%20their%20share%20of%20money%20from%20here.%20The%20incident%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%20by%20NIA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20leader%20Subhendu%20Adhikari%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSuvenduWB%2Fstatus%2F1695844457520955456%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Edemanded%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20NIA%20investigation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20North%20and%20South%2024%20Parganas%2C%20hundreds%20of%20illegal%20firecrackers%20and%20crude%20bomb-making%20factories%20have%20been%20thriving.%20The%20factory%20in%20Duttapukur%20used%20to%20employ%20close%20to%20100%20local%20women%20who%20were%20engaged%20in%20packing%20%E2%80%98firecrackers%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ruling%20party%20is%20directly%20involved%20in%20this%20illegal%20activity.%20They%20have%20been%20collecting%20%3Cem%3Ehaftas%3C%2Fem%3E%20regularly%20from%20these%20illegal%20bomb%20makers.%20There%20was%20an%20explosion%20four%20years%20back.%20When%20locals%20protested%2C%20police%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20leaders%20threatened%20locals%20and%20detained%20them%20under%20false%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20CPI%20(M)%20state%20secretary%20Md%20Salim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20Rahman%20and%20Ali%2C%20the%20TMC%20activists%20who%20allegedly%20ran%20the%20factory%2C%20were%20arrested%20in%20the%20past%20but%20got%20bail%20due%20to%20diluted%20charges.%20A%20similar%20pattern%20was%20observed%20in%20Egra%20as%20well%2C%20where%20the%20factory%20owner%20Bhanu%20Bag%20resumed%20illegal%20firecracker%20manufacturing%20after%20being%20released%20on%20bail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLeaders%20like%20Ali%20supply%20the%20poor%20families%20with%20bombs%20and%20fireworks%20materials.%20The%20more%20they%20make%2C%20the%20more%20they%20earn.%20What%20will%20the%20poor%20do%3F%20There%20are%20families%20where%20everyone%20is%20working%20for%20these%20illegal%20factories%2C%20but%20no%20one%20will%20admit%20it%20in%20public.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20demand%20for%20crude%20bombs%20and%20firecrackers%20until%20next%20April-May.%20A%20family%20can%20earn%20Rs%208%2C000-10%2C000%20a%20month%20by%20working%20all%20day.%20But%20the%20factory%20owners%20make%20the%20real%20money.%20They%20quickly%20become%20rich%2C%E2%80%9D%20explained%20Samshuddin%20Qazi%2C%20a%20local%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20both%20Egra%20and%20Duttapukur%2C%20villagers%20were%20compelled%20to%20engage%20in%20unlawful%20activities%20out%20of%20desperation%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20legitimate%20employment%20opportunities.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20rural%20economy%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20under%20considerable%20strain%2C%20despite%20claims%20of%20development%20and%20progress.%20The%20lack%20of%20sustained%20efforts%20to%20create%20meaningful%20employment%20opportunities%20has%20led%20to%20a%20vacuum%20that%20illegal%20activities%20are%20increasingly%20filling.%20The%20gradual%20decline%20in%20funds%20allocated%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%C2%A0MGNREGA%20has%20further%20worsened%20this%20situation%2C%20a%20fact%20used%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20to%20shift%20the%20blame.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20usual%20tactic%20of%20finger-pointing%20at%20the%20state%20government%2C%20LoP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSuvenduWB%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40SuvenduWB%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20conveniently%20forgotten%20to%20mention%20that%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%F0%9F%91%89Those%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20Egra%20were%20driven%20to%20hazardous%20work%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20under%20the%20100%20days%20of%20work%20scheme%20whose%20funds%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpkbMxsHlJ7%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FpkbMxsHlJ7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20(%40KunalGhoshAgain)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKunalGhoshAgain%2Fstatus%2F1695769689279078419%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndraneel%20Dasgupta%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20ISI%20Kolkata%2C%20said%20that%20e%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Every%20time%20there%20is%20an%20unfortunate%20incident%20in%20Bengal%20or%20one%20that%20involves%20Bengalis%2C%20the%20state%20government%20and%20ruling%20party%20leaders%20tend%20to%20attribute%20it%20to%20the%20freezing%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%E2%80%99s%20true%20that%20the%20fund%20freeze%20is%20impacting%20the%20rural%20population%20of%20the%20state%2C%20it%20highlights%20a%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government%20to%20create%20sufficient%20employment%20opportunities.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20Coromandel%20accident%2C%20the%20Mizoram%20bridge%20collapse%2C%20or%20the%20explosion%20in%20the%20crude%20bomb%20factory%2C%20the%20authorities%20are%20resorting%20to%20the%20same%20explanation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dasgupta%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20pattern%20suggests%20that%20the%20rural%20economy%20in%20the%20state%20is%20facing%20significant%20challenges%2C%20despite%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20lofty%20claims.%20Unfortunately%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20lack%20of%20substantial%20efforts%20to%20generate%20meaningful%20rural%20employment.%20There%20are%20two%20options%20left%20to%20the%20rural%20people%3A%20seasonal%20migration%20to%20southern%20states%20where%20the%20average%20wage%20is%20almost%20double%20that%20in%20West%20Bengal%20or%20work%20in%20illegal%20or%20hazardous%20trade%20like%20firecracker%20factories%20for%20livelihood%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20professor%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20West%20Bengal%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20a%20series%20of%20explosions.%20These%20incidents%20lay%20bare%20the%20vulnerabilities%20of%20a%20population%20caught%20between%20a%20lack%20of%20legitimate%20livelihoods%20and%20the%20pervasive%20risks%20of%20illegal%20activities.%20Below%20is%20a%20timeline%20of%20these%20events%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAugust%2027%3A%20An%20explosion%20occurred%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20worker%2C%20claiming%20nine%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%2030%3A%20A%20student%20from%20the%20fourth%20grade%2C%20Yousuf%20Mandal%2C%20lost%20his%20hand%20due%20to%20an%20explosion%20caused%20by%20a%20bomb-making%20attempt%20in%20Golbagan%2C%20Ward%202%20of%20Basirhat%20Municipality.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%2026%3A%20An%20explosion%20occurred%20in%20the%20house%20of%20Trinamool%20leader%20Golam%20Rasul%20in%20Hazrapur%20village%20of%20Dubrajpur.%20Bomb-making%20activities%20were%20reportedly%20underway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%203%3A%20An%20attempt%20to%20make%20a%20bomb%20resulted%20in%20an%20explosion%20that%20claimed%20the%20life%20of%20Trinamool%20worker%20Paritosh%20Mondal%20in%20Kuchiya%20Moda%20village%20of%20Haldia%20Block.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EJune%205%3A%20A%20teenager%20lost%20his%20life%20in%20Ward%2010%20of%20Bongaon%20due%20to%20a%20bomb%20explosion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%2023%3A%20A%20bomb%20explosion%20in%20English%20Bazar%20took%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20van%20drivers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%2022%3A%20A%20blast%20took%20place%20in%20the%20house%20of%20a%20Trinamool%20worker%20in%20Ghodapara-Kolai%20Danga%20village%2C%20Dubrajpur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%2021%3A%20An%20illegal%20bomb-making%20factory%20in%20Bajbaj%E2%80%99s%20Nandarampur%20Daspara%20exploded%2C%20claiming%20three%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%2018%3A%20Laily%20Bibi%2C%20a%20Trinamool%20member%2C%20lost%20her%20life%20due%20to%20an%20explosion%20in%20Raghunathganj%2C%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMay%2016%3A%20A%20massive%20explosion%20occurred%20in%20an%20illegal%20firecracker%20factory%20associated%20with%20a%20Trinamool%20leader%20in%20Egra.%20The%20incident%20claimed%20nine%20lives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693222527000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28165052%2Fimage1-2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwest-bengal-illegal-firecracker-factories-rural-distress%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20latest%20explosion%20on%20Sunday%2C%20at%20least%20eight%20people%20were%20killed.%20While%20experts%20point%20to%20rural%20distress%20forcing%20vulnerable%20populations%20to%20take%20up%20dangerous%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20locals%20also%20say%20the%20factories%20have%20political%20patronage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwest-bengal-illegal-firecracker-factories-rural-distress%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sebi%20notifies%20stricter%20delisting%20rules%20for%20non-convertible%20debt%20securities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693222512000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F31%2Ffull%2F1685549430-5238.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fsebi-notifies-stricter-delisting-rules-for-non-convertible-debt-securities-123082800717_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20its%20notification%20issued%20on%20August%2023%2C%20Sebi%20said%20the%20new%20framework%20for%20delisting%20of%20non-convertible%20debt%20securities%20would%20allow%20all%20listed%20non-co