supreme-court-for-article-370-hearing%5C%22%3E%20after%20he%20appeared%20before%20the%20court%20in%20the%20Article%20370%20hearings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%20apprised%20the%20court%20of%20Zahoor%20Ahmad%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20suspension.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fwhy-lecturer-suspended-soon-after-appearing-in-article-370-case-supreme-court-asks-jk-administration-236345%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20academic%20had%20taken%20leave%20for%20two%20days%20to%20appear%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20had%20been%20suspended%20on%20his%20return.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unfair%2C%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20AG%20will%20look%20at%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20told%20AG%20R.%20Venkataramani%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter%20when%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20interjected%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fwhy-lecturer-suspended-soon-after-appearing-in-article-370-case-supreme-court-asks-jk-administration-236345%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20checked%20up%20after%20having%20read%20in%20the%20newspapers.%20What%20is%20reported%20in%20the%20newspapers%20may%20not%20be%20the%20whole%20truth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibal%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20August%2025%20order%20made%20a%20reference%20to%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Farticle-370-hearing-day-9-extreme-examples-extreme-cases%5C%22%3EArticle%20370%20Hearing%3A%20SC%20Told%20Extreme%20Examples%20Are%20Necessary%20To%20Solve%20Extreme%20Cases%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20argued%20that%20Bhat%20appears%20in%20various%20courts%20and%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cother%20issues%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThen%20he%20should%20have%20been%20suspended%20earlier%2C%20why%20now%3F%20This%20is%20not%20fair.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way%20democracy%20should%20function%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sibal%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTalk%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20and%20see%20what%20has%20happened.%20If%20there%20is%20something%20apart%20from%20this%2C%20then%20it%20is%20different.%20But%20why%20this%20in%20close%20succession%20to%20him%20appearing%20in%20the%20matter%3F%E2%80%9D%20CJI%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kishan%20Kaul%20said%20that%20if%20the%20letter%20of%20suspension%20has%20reference%20to%20his%20appearance%2C%20then%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20a%20problem%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20BR%20Gavai%2C%20who%20is%20also%20on%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20hearing%20the%20Article%20370%20petitions%2C%20said%20that%20the%20government%20action%20may%20be%20a%20retribution%2C%20%E2%80%9DWhat%20happens%20to%20so%20much%20freedom%20then%E2%80%A6%20if%20it%20has%20happened%20due%20to%20appearance%20here%20then%20it%20is%20indeed%20retribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhat%2C%20also%20an%20advocate%20who%20teaches%20political%20science%20at%20the%20Srinagar%20school%2C%20had%20told%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20challenging%20situation%20for%20educators%20like%20me%20when%20we%20teach%20the%20principles%20of%20this%20beautiful%20constitution%20and%20the%20ideals%20of%20democracy%20to%20our%20students%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Students%20often%20pose%20a%20difficult%20question%20%E2%80%93%20are%20we%20still%20a%20democracy%20after%20the%20events%20of%20August%2C%202019%3F%20Answering%20this%20question%20becomes%20extremely%20complex%20and%20challenging%20for%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fsrinagar%2Fjk-lecturer-suspended-for-appearing-in-sc-arguing-for-petitioners-in-article-370-case-8909821%2F%5C%22%3Esuspended%20Bhat%20for%20allegedly%20violating%20the%20provisions%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Civil%20Service%20Rules%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Government%20Employees%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C1971%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Principal%20Secretary%2C%20School%20Education%2C%20Alok%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPending%20enquiry%20into%20his%20conduct%2C%20the%20delinquent%20officer%20%E2%80%A6%20is%20hereby%20placed%20under%20suspension%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20He%20shall%20remain%20attached%20in%20the%20office%20of%20Director%20School%20Education%2C%20Jammu%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20order%20stated%2C%20while%20appointing%20Subah%20Mehta%2C%20Joint%20Director%2C%20School%20Education%2C%20Jammu%20as%20inquiry%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Section%2016%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Government%20Employees%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C1971%2C%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20necessary%E2%80%9D%20for%20an%20employee%20to%20%E2%80%9Cobtain%20permission%20for%20initiating%20proceedings%20in%20a%20Court%20of%20law%20in%20matters%20other%20than%20vindication%20of%20his%20official%20act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2018%20of%20the%20act%20bars%20employees%20from%20criticising%20the%20government%20in%20%E2%80%9Cany%20public%20utterance%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20sub-section%201%20of%20Section%2018%2C%20%E2%80%9Chas%20the%20effect%20of%20an%20adverse%20criticism%20of%20any%20current%20or%20recent%20policy%20or%20action%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20Government%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20or%20any%20other%20State%20Government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhat%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20evoked%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20National%20Conference%20vice-president%20Omar%20Abdullah%20and%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20who%20said%20that%20the%20action%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%20was%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20illegal%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20have%20to%20choose.%20Either%20be%20mute%20spectators%20and%20watch%20their%20livelihood%2C%20jobs%20and%20land%20being%20snatched%20or%20face%20the%20music%20for%20raising%20their%20voice.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Hobson%E2%80%99s%20choice%20laden%20with%20deadly%20consequences.%20Every%20Kashmiri%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20knock%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20SC%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mehbooba%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20thanked%20Sibal%20for%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20Bhat%E2%80%99s%20suspension%20in%20the%20apex%20court.%20%E2%80%9DGrateful%20to%20Kapil%20Sibal%20for%20raising%20the%20issue%20of%20Zahoor%20Bhat%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Zahoor%20is%20a%20lecturer%20who%20was%20suspended%20immediately%20after%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20valley%20having%20argued%20his%20petition%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20against%20the%20events%20of%20Aug%205%2C%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20Omar%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Jehangir%20Ali.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693219510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-asks-ag-to-look-into-suspension-of-jk-lecturer-after-his-appearance-in-article-370-hearing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20teach%20the%20ideals%20of%20democracy%20to%20our%20students%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zahoor%20Ahmad%20Bhatt%20had%20said%20in%20court%20a%20day%20before%20his%20suspension.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22