ads%2F2023%2F08%2F28142902%2FRIGHT-TO-INFORMATION.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20Online%20website%2C%20the%20portal%20used%20by%20ordinary%20citizens%20to%20file%20Right%20to%20Information%20applications%20related%20to%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20has%20been%20structurally%20rendered%20useless%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20It%20started%20with%20modifications%20to%20the%20website%20which%20removed%20the%20signing%20up%20process%20to%20create%20an%20account%20and%20repeated%20warnings%20that%20old%2C%20unused%20accounts%20would%20be%20deleted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frti-portal-rtionline-years-of-information-disappears%5C%22%3Erecent%20deletion%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20since%20overturned%20%E2%80%93%20to%20remove%20all%20RTI%20applications%20prior%20to%202022%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20many%20as%20it%20was%20done%20with%20no%20notice.%20Many%20feared%20that%20this%20information%20was%20lost%20forever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERTI%20Online%20has%20now%20restored%20all%20the%20deleted%20RTIs%20and%20the%20website%20displays%20the%20following%20message%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20data%20prior%20to%20year%202022%20was%20moved%20to%20an%20archival%20database%20for%20better%20performance%20and%20manageability.%20This%20archived%20data%20was%20not%20visible%20on%20the%20portal%20during%20this%20activity.%20The%20complete%20data%20for%20RTI%20Request%20and%20Appeal%20has%20been%20plugged%20in%20now%20and%20is%20available%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20could%20have%20been%20multiple%20reasons%20%E2%80%93%20technical%20and%20administrative%20%E2%80%93%20for%20why%20the%20information%20was%20%E2%80%98temporarily%E2%80%99%20removed.%20Often%2C%20maintenance%20activity%20of%20digital%20services%20can%20make%20them%20temporarily%20unavailable.%20While%20this%20is%20an%20accepted%20practice%20within%20software%20development%20cycles%2C%20such%20activities%20usually%20come%20with%20intimation%20or%20prior%20notice%20%E2%80%93%20which%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20do.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChanges%20made%20to%20the%20RTI%20Online%20website%20have%20always%20been%20sudden%20and%20with%20no%20explanation%20offered.%20For%20example%2C%20let%20us%20consider%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20signing-up%20form%20to%20create%20new%20user%20accounts.%20This%20small%20change%20effectively%20disallowed%20people%20from%20creating%20a%20new%20account%20and%20made%20tracking%20RTI%20applications%20a%20lot%20more%20complicated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Right%20to%20Information%20request%20by%20the%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20filed%20in%202021%20asked%20about%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20the%20signing-up%20form.%20The%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20(DoPT)%20did%20not%20give%20any%20actual%20explanation%20in%20response.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20response%20to%20our%20RTI%20on%20the%20disallowance%20of%20new%20users%20to%20register%20and%20the%20UI%20change%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNICMeity%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40NICMeity%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20said%20they%20do%20not%20have%20any%20material%20information%20on%20changes%20made%20to%20the%20RTI%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoin%20us%20on%20our%20forum%20and%20advance%20the%20conversation!%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0vMcEwr0GE%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0vMcEwr0GE%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Internet%20Freedom%20Foundation%20(IFF)%20(%40internetfreedom)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Finternetfreedom%2Fstatus%2F1474319599705333765%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2024%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20software%20development%20cycles%2C%20institutions%20and%20projects%20maintain%20a%20log%20of%20changes%20that%20were%20made%20to%20the%20software%20release%20management%20called%20%E2%80%9Cchangelog%E2%80%9D.%20The%20changelog%20is%20the%20place%20where%20software%20engineers%20keep%20track%20of%20all%20changes%20being%20made%20to%20the%20software%20and%20why%20that%20change%20has%20been%20made.%20The%20practice%20may%20vary%20from%20one%20institution%20to%20the%20next%20as%20per%20their%20requirements%2C%20but%20the%20goal%20remains%20the%20same%3A%20retaining%20institutional%20memory%20about%20the%20software.%20Clearly%2C%20neither%20the%20DoPT%20nor%20the%20National%20Informatics%20Centre%20(NIC)%20maintain%20these%20records.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20these%20structural%20changes%20to%20how%20the%20website%20functions%2C%20other%20errors%20%E2%80%93%20with%20payment%20processing%20and%20the%20general%20unresponsiveness%20of%20the%20portal%20%E2%80%93%20also%20made%20it%20practically%20unusable.%20While%20these%20issues%20are%20not%20new%2C%20DoPT%20and%20NIC%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20never%20acknowledged%20their%20responsibility%20to%20fix%20them%2C%20which%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealways%20a%20source%20of%20concern.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28141229%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22725%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28141229%2Funnamed.jpg%20512w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28141229%2Funnamed-300x107.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670207%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22259%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20message%20from%20RTI%20Online%20when%20payment%20processing%20fails.%20Photo%3A%20Srinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20failure%20of%20%E2%80%98Digital%20India%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20the%20lack%20of%20accountability%20when%20software%20fails.%20Every%20software%20engineer%20understands%20that%20systems%20sometimes%20fail%20and%20that%20they%20need%20to%20design%20mechanisms%20to%20tackle%20such%20scenarios.%20From%20internal%20errors%20to%20third-party%20software%20%E2%80%93%20like%20payment%20processors%20or%20OTP%20gateways%20going%20through%20maintenance%2C%20there%20are%20several%20factors%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20private%20software%20organisations%20and%20institutions%20follow%20software%20development%20practices%20that%20help%20ensure%20the%20quality%20of%20software%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20lead%20to%20system%20failures.%20However%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20accountability%20within%20all%20government%20institutions%20%E2%80%93%20that%20stems%20right%20from%20the%20top%20%E2%80%93%20means%20that%20even%20if%20there%20are%20solutions%20to%20these%20problems%2C%20they%20are%20not%20implemented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%20of%20lack%20of%20software%20accountability%2C%20the%20future%20of%20RTI%20Online%20%E2%80%93%20and%20RTI%20at%20large%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20at%20stake.%20Often%2C%20people%20propose%20privatisation%20of%20government%20services%20to%20address%20the%20inefficiencies%20in%20the%20system.%20Such%20a%20model%20may%20not%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20lack%20of%20accountability%20because%20the%20private%20sector%E2%80%99s%20priority%20is%20to%20make%20profits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThose%20who%20use%20RTI%20must%20be%20prepared%20for%20RTI%20Online%20to%20be%20completely%20shut%20down.%20The%20preparation%20can%20begin%20with%3C%2Fspan%3E%20archiving%20all%20the%20existing%20information%20on%20an%20alternative%20storage%20system%20that%20is%20not%20dependent%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RTI%20community%20also%20has%20to%20ensure%20that%20rights%20in%20cyberspace%20are%20advanced%20by%20demanding%20electronic%20information%20and%20software%20code.%20Digitisation%20has%20made%20government%20systems%20invisible%20and%20the%20RTI%20community%20has%20to%20push%20for%20transparency%20in%20this%20domain%20too%2C%20as%20it%20battles%20to%20preserve%20this%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693214967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28142902%2FRIGHT-TO-INFORMATION.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frti-online-lack-of-accountability-future%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20biggest%20failure%20of%20'Digital%20India'%20has%20been%20the%20lack%20of%20accountability%20when%20software%20fails.%20The%20Union%20government's%20portal%20to%20file%20RTI%20requests%20has%20been%20plagued%20with%20errors%20for%20years%2C%20none%20of%20which%20have%20been%20fixed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en