Famp_articleshow%2F103132195.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20court%20drops%20murder%20abetment%20charges%20against%20Imran%20Khan%20-%20lawyer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693213403000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103132361%2Cimgsize-738760.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-drops-sedition-charges-against-former-pm-imran-khan%2Farticleshow%2F103132195.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103132195.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20court%20in%20Pakistan%20on%20Monday%20dismissed%20a%20sedition%20case%20against%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20his%20lawyer%20said%20on%20messaging%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-drops-sedition-charges-against-former-pm-imran-khan%2Farticleshow%2F103132195.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-drops-sedition-charges-against-former-pm-imran-khan%2Famp_articleshow%2F103132195.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-court-drops-sedition-charges-against-former-pm-imran-khan%2Famp_articleshow%2F103132195.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Archaeology%20of%20a%20Disaster%20in%20Shiv%20Baodi%2C%20Summerhill%3A%20A%20Photo-Chronicle%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132623%2FDSC_0279.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EObsessed%20as%20I%20have%20been%20with%20my%20camera%20(or%20any%20instrument%20with%20a%20camera%20in%20it)%2C%20there%20were%20other%20things%20I%20just%20began%20to%20freeze%20about%20this%20neighbourhood%20I%20arrived%20in%20only%20in%20January%20this%20year%20and%20in%20a%20different%20mental%20space.%20There%20were%20some%20more%20dramatic%20trees%20and%20creepers%20and%20the%20train%20(6%3A15%20pm%20and%207%3A15%20pm)%20that%20Oli%2C%20my%20canine%20significant%20other%20and%20I%2C%20walked%20past%20every%20morning%20and%20evening%20to%20be%20frozen%2C%20yet%2C%20as%20images%2C%20histories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20got%20late%20for%20the%20walk%20that%20fateful%20morning%20on%20August%2014.%20To%20think%20that%20just%20last%20month%2C%20I%20photographed%20the%20train%20track%20en%20route%20Boileauganj%2C%20and%20a%20few%20Deodars%20with%20character%2C%20and%20Oli%20waiting%20for%20a%20train.%20Today%2C%20that%20path%2C%20and%20train%20track%2C%20are%20out%20of%20access%20for%20ordinary%20people%20like%20us.%20Strange%20it%20seems%20to%20me%20that%20of%20all%20the%20things%2C%20I%20lost%20the%20only%20pictures%20of%20the%20old%20temple%20and%20the%20last%20%3Cem%3Ebhandara%3C%2Fem%3E%20(feast)%20held%20there%20around%20the%20month%20of%20May%2C%20when%20my%20older%20phone%20lost%20its%20life%20in%20in%20a%20freak%20water-related%20accident%20in%20late%20June%20at%20a%20village%20in%20Dharamshala.%20Sometimes%2C%20things%20lost%20in%20a%20gush%20of%20water%20never%20return%2C%20and%20if%20they%20do%2C%20they%20come%20back%20not%20quite%20the%20same%20again%2C%20as%20it%20happened%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20event%20now%20seems%20ominous%20and%20most%20disconcerting%2C%20on%20hindsight.%20The%20only%20image%20that%20I%20now%20have%20is%20of%20the%20smaller%20one%20(with%20meanings%20and%20stories%20that%20people%20share%20everyday)%20built%20by%20Saunkhi%20Ram%20and%20his%20wife%20Shanta%2C%20a%20rare%20structure%20built%20with%20images%20of%20Shiva%2C%20Parvati%20and%20Ganesha%20in%20vernacular%20style%2C%20by%20a%20Dalit%20person%2C%20sitting%20pretty%20with%20the%20older%20structure%2C%20and%20yet%20where%20many%2C%20including%20the%20Pandit%20ji%20(Suman%20Kishore%2C%20who%20died%20in%20the%20disaster)%20offered%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meaning%20of%20life%2C%20it%20appears%2C%20is%20not%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20present%20moment%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20perfect%20for%20an%20image%2C%20or%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20to%20simply%20let%20go%20of%20an%20image%20that%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20be%20frozen.%20Permanence%20is%20an%20illusion%20and%20one%20feels%20it%20every%20night%20when%20the%20sky%20rumbles%2C%20the%20lightning%20strikes%20and%20the%20downpour%20starts%2C%20and%20the%20earth%20seems%20to%20shift%20a%20bit%20uneasily%20underneath%2C%20perhaps%20in%20her%20longer%20geological%20journey%20that%20we%20have%20no%20idea%20about.%20Who%20would%20have%20believed%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20Prospect%20Hill%2C%20not%20far%20from%20here%2C%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20volcano%2C%20or%20that%20Shimla%20sat%20on%20a%20sea%20on%20whose%20surface%20icebergs%20once%20floated!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20much%20longer%20history%20that%20we%20seem%20to%20have%20no%20control%20over%2C%20yet%20in%20the%20shorter%20span%20of%20ephemeral%20lives%2C%20we%20come%20to%20believe%20we%20can%20make%20plains%20out%20of%20mountains%20and%20reach%20the%20moon%E2%80%A6%20Yet%2C%20yet%2C%20it%20took%20all%20of%2011%20days%20to%20retrieve%20just%2020%20bodies%20(none%20alive)%20within%20a%20small%20radius%20of%203-4%20km%20for%20an%20army%20of%20men%20from%20the%20SDRF%2C%20NDRF%2C%20police%20personnel%20and%20several%20local%20people%20from%20in%20and%20around%20Summerhill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20questions%20arose%20in%20my%20head%20as%20I%20ran%20up%20and%20downhill%20with%20different%20groups%20of%20search%20teams%20all%20of%20the%20past%2011%20days%2C%20starting%20around%2010%20am%20and%20reaching%20home%20around%206%20pm%2C%20some%20of%20which%20remain%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98natural%20calamity%E2%80%99%20not%20take%20away%20the%20issue%20from%20human%20responsibility%20and%20over-interference%20in%20the%20natural%20world%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20to%20say%20of%20the%20length%20of%20time%20that%20the%20ground%20in%20the%20IIAS%20was%20sinking%20or%20under%20repair%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20large%20fissures%20on%20the%20path%20through%20the%20forest%20in%20the%20premises%20have%20been%20happening%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20unnoticed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20does%20a%20tourist%20obsess%20about%20reaching%20Manali%20or%20Shimla%20from%20Chandigarh%20in%20a%20jiffy%20for%20a%20holiday%3F%20Why%20does%20fast-tracking%20a%20road%20journey%20matter%20so%20much%3F%20What%20necessitated%20the%20four-lanes%20for%20a%20small%20hilly%20region%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20the%20four-lane%20highway%20projects%20started%20the%20process%20of%20slow%20death%20of%20the%20precious%20mountains%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhere%20are%20the%20true%20cracks%20on%20the%20earth%E2%80%99s%20surface%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20ripple%20effect%20impacting%20entire%20Himachal%20so%20badly%3F%20Is%20excessive%20rainfall%20and%20%E2%80%98cloud%20burst%E2%80%99%20the%20only%20geological%2Fmeteorological%20explanation%20left%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20to%20say%20of%20the%20drilling%20(as%20popular%20opinion%20now%20makes%20itself%20audible%20and%20visible%2C%20after%20the%20tragedy%2C%20unfortunately)%20of%20the%20rockface%20behind%20the%20temple%20for%20building%20a%20new%2C%20taller%20Hanuman%20temple%20next%20to%20the%20Shiva%20temple%3F%20Can%20small%2C%20unassuming%20shrines%20of%20faith%20remain%20small%20and%20unassuming%2C%20or%20does%20everything%20have%20to%20be%20larger%20than%20life%3F%20Is%20there%20any%20role%20of%20the%20new%20construction%20on%20the%20space%20in%20the%20matter%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20new%20temple%20contractor%20(many%20local%20stories%20abound)%20pay%20a%20visit%20even%20to%20offer%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20bereaved%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20the%20Union%20government%20(reported%20in%20the%20media)%20proposing%20to%20construct%20a%20massive%20international%20sports%20complex%20near%20the%20Indrunag%20temple%20near%20Dharamshala%2C%20considering%20its%20fragile%20ecosystem%20and%20the%20massive%20deforestation%20that%20will%20ensue%20in%20a%20prone%20to%20flash-flood%20area%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20government%20commence%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20constructions%20that%20came%20up%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20(even%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20many%20new%20buildings%20sprouted%20up%3F)%20and%20an%20audit%20of%20the%20older%20buildings%20that%20were%20unsafe%20allowed%20to%20exist%2C%20with%20residents%20living%20in%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20there%20be%20a%20comprehensive%20inquiry%20into%20the%20nature%20of%20spending%20on%20restoration%20works%20in%20IIAS%20premises%2C%20which%20houses%20only%20a%20few%20fellows%20but%20a%20larger%20number%20of%20(more%20importantly)%20staff%20(contractual%20and%20regular)%20across%20designations%20within%20the%20premises%3F%20How%20important%20is%20the%20institutional%20working%20class%20for%20government%20institutions%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20the%20entire%20city%20of%20Shimla%20in%20grave%20danger%2C%20considering%20the%20collapse%20of%20few%20structures%20and%20declaration%20of%20few%20others%20as%20unsafe%2C%20even%20as%20roads%20have%20been%20caving%20in%20at%20several%20locations%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20railway%20minister%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20disaster%20sites%2C%20which%20included%20the%20heritage%20structures%20of%20IIAS%20and%20the%20UNESCO%20heritage%20Shimla-Kalka%20rail%20line%2C%20when%20otherwise%20you%20saw%20them%20feverishly%20inaugurating%20every%20Vande%20Bharat%20express%20everywhere%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20didn%E2%80%99t%20the%20director%20of%20IIAS%20feel%20it%20necessary%20to%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20disaster%20site%20in%20a%20suburb%20not%20far%20from%20the%20institute%2C%20even%20if%20to%20offer%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20some%20questions%20for%20all%20(apology%20Dylan)%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20years%20can%20a%20mountain%20exist%2C%20before%20it%E2%80%99s%20washed%20%5Bin%20the%20greed%20of%20the%20political%20class%2C%20the%20contractors%2C%20and%20the%20consumption-tourists%5D%20to%20the%20sea%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20deaths%20will%20it%20take%20till%20%5Bwe%5D%20know%2C%20that%20too%20many%20people%20have%20died%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20answer%E2%80%A6is%20blowin%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%E2%80%A6%20across%20rivers%20and%20clouds%20and%20mountains%20and%20the%20earth%20beneath%20our%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20long%20will%20it%20take%20for%20us%20to%20hear%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20it%2C%20I%20let%20the%20images%20tell%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERelief%20efforts%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F28132610%2FDSC_0278-1024x681.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-670178%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22798%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2