%2F30134445%2FScreenshot-2022-07-30-at-1.44.32-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20police%20have%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Mohammed%20Zubair%2C%20a%20fact-checker%20and%20journalist%20with%20%3Cem%3EAlt%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20for%20sharing%20the%20video%20of%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%20who%20was%20slapped%20by%20his%20classmates%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20their%20school%20teacher%20recently.%20Zubair%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20an%20FIR%20had%20been%20lodged%20against%20him%20even%20though%20he%20had%20later%20deleted%20the%20video%20and%20notified%20his%20followers%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20accuses%20Zubair%20of%20revealing%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20boy%20through%20the%20act%20of%20sharing%20the%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20online.%20The%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20at%20the%20Mansoorpur%20police%20station%20in%20the%20western%20UP%20district%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20August%2028%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20one%20Vishnudutt%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20village%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZubair%2C%20who%20is%20often%20on%20the%20radar%20of%20right-wing%20forces%20as%20well%20as%20BJP-ruled%20state%20governments%2C%20was%20charged%20under%20Section%2074%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015%2C%20which%20is%20punishable%20by%20imprisonment%20up%20to%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2025%2C%20Zubair%20had%20put%20out%20a%20tweet%20of%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20father%20narrating%20that%20he%20had%20decided%20to%20not%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20against%20the%20teacher%20for%20making%20other%20students%20hit%20his%20son.%20Zubair%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20not%20only%20disclosed%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20man%20but%20also%20of%20his%20minor%20son.%20However%2C%20hours%20later%20Zubair%20deleted%20the%20video%20after%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20had%20asked%20people%20not%20to%20share%20the%20video%20and%20warned%20them%20that%20revealing%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20boy%20was%20an%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZubair%20was%20amazed%20that%20even%20though%20the%20video%20was%20widely%20shared%20by%20thousands%20of%20other%20people%2C%20including%20journalists%20and%20politicians%2C%20he%20was%20singled%20out%20by%20the%20police%20for%20action%2C%20despite%20deleting%20his%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20feel%20it%20is%20vendetta%20politics.%20Soon%20after%20the%20NCPCR%20asked%20people%20to%20not%20share%20the%20video%2C%20I%20deleted%20the%20video%20and%20pointed%20it%20out%20on%20my%20timeline.%20But%20I%20was%20singled%20out.%20Several%20other%20TV%20channels%20and%20anchors%20played%20the%20video%20before%20and%20after%20I%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20Zubair%20told%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Station%20House%20Officer%20of%20Mansoorpur%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20phone%20calls.%20Zubair%20says%20the%20police%20are%20yet%20to%20approach%20him.%20He%20is%20taking%20legal%20advice%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20several%20rights%20activists%20have%20questioned%20why%20the%20teacher%20in%20question%20%E2%80%93%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20%E2%80%93%20has%20only%20been%20charged%20with%20non-cognisable%20offences%20under%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20viral%20video%20which%20the%20government%20authorities%20have%20now%20had%20removed%20from%20social%20media%2C%20Tyagi%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Neha%20Public%20School%20at%20her%20home%2C%20can%20be%20seen%20exhorting%20other%20students%20to%20assault%20a%20Muslim%20child%20who%20is%20seen%20crying%20while%20different%20students%20come%20forward%C2%A0%20to%20slap%20him.%20At%20one%20point%20in%20the%20video%2C%20the%20teacher%20scolded%20a%20student%20for%20not%20hitting%20him%20hard%20enough.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20declared%20that%20all%20those%20Muslim%20children%20should%20be%E2%80%A6(inaudible)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20can%20be%20heard%20saying%20in%20the%2040-second-long%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fup-pressure-on-boys-family-to-compromise-in-slapping-incident-as-politicians-swarm-the-village%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20has%20been%20pressure%20on%20the%20young%20boy%E2%80%99s%20family%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccompromise%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20take%20charges%20against%20the%20teacher%20forward.%20Tyagi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fslapping-muzaffarnagar-school-student-muslim-tripti-tyagi%5C%22%3Ehas%20claimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20she%20did%20nothing%20wrong%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20communal%20about%20her%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZubair%20was%20arrested%20and%20put%20in%20jail%20for%20three%20weeks%20in%20June-July%202022%2C%20and%20multiple%20cases%20filed%20against%20him%20for%20a%20tweet%20in%20which%20he%20had%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20from%20an%20old%20Bollywood%20film.%20He%20was%20released%20on%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693212349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F30134445%2FScreenshot-2022-07-30-at-1.44.32-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fvendetta-up-police-files-fir-against-alt-news-journalist-for-tweet-on-muslim-boy-slapped%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Zubair%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20an%20FIR%20had%20been%20lodged%20against%20him%20even%20though%20he%20had%20later%20deleted%20the%20video%20and%20notified%20his%20followers%20on%20social%20media%20site%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fvendetta-up-police-files-fir-against-alt-news-journ