.com%2F%3Fp%3D327829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lilyma%20Khan%20is%20the%20head%20chef%20at%20Dear%20Donna%20in%20Delhi.%20She%20recalls%20the%20struggle%20she%20faced%20to%20get%20here%2C%20how%20her%20love%20for%20cooking%20came%20to%20be%2C%20and%20how%20she%20forged%20past%20all%20the%20obstacles%20that%20life%20threw%20her%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327829%2Flilyma-khan-head-chef-at-dear-donna-delhi-shares-struggle-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20Say%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20Death%20Sentence%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20I%20Wish%20People%20Knew%20About%20Living%20with%20HIV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Homophobia%2C%20bullying%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20myths%20associated%20with%20HIV%20is%20that%20it%20is%20a%20death%20sentence.%20%5BBut%5D%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20those%20who%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20the%20treatment.%20HIV%20is%20not%20the%20end%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Gautam%20Yadav%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Delhi%2C%20has%20been%20living%20with%20HIV%20since%20the%20age%20of%2018.%20Since%20his%20diagnosis%2C%20he%20has%20dedicated%20his%20life%20to%20spreading%20awareness%20of%20the%20disease%20and%20shattering%20the%20myths%20surrounding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20actor%2C%20and%20was%20taking%20singing%20and%20theatre%20classes.%20When%20I%20was%20diagnosed%2C%20I%20was%20just%2018%2C%20and%20I%20thought%20I%E2%80%99d%2C%20too%2C%20die%20soon%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BBut%5D%20I%20realised%20that%20there%20must%20be%20other%20Gautams%2C%20who%20are%20very%20young%20and%20m